7120- (void)_updateSelectionAssistantSuppressionState
7121{
7122 static const double minimumFocusedElementAreaForSuppressingSelectionAssistant = 4;
7123
7124 auto& editorState = _page->editorState();
7125 if (editorState.isMissingPostLayoutData)
7126 return;
7127
7128 BOOL editableRootIsTransparentOrFullyClipped = NO;
7129 BOOL focusedElementIsTooSmall = NO;
7130 if (!editorState.selectionIsNone) {
7131 auto& postLayoutData = editorState.postLayoutData();
7132 if (postLayoutData.editableRootIsTransparentOrFullyClipped)
7133 editableRootIsTransparentOrFullyClipped = YES;
7134
7135 if (self._hasFocusedElement) {
7136 auto elementArea = postLayoutData.selectionClipRect.area<RecordOverflow>();
7137 if (!elementArea.hasOverflowed() && elementArea < minimumFocusedElementAreaForSuppressingSelectionAssistant)
7138 focusedElementIsTooSmall = YES;
7139 }
7140 }
7141
7142 if (editableRootIsTransparentOrFullyClipped)
7143 [self _startSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:WebKit::EditableRootIsTransparentOrFullyClipped];
7144 else
7145 [self _stopSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:WebKit::EditableRootIsTransparentOrFullyClipped];
7146
7147 if (focusedElementIsTooSmall)
7148 [self _startSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:WebKit::FocusedElementIsTooSmall];
7149 else
7150 [self _stopSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:WebKit::FocusedElementIsTooSmall];
7151}
7152
7153- (void)_selectionChanged
7154{
7155#if ENABLE(APP_HIGHLIGHTS)
7156 [self setUpAppHighlightMenusIfNeeded];
7157#endif
7158
7159 [self _updateSelectionAssistantSuppressionState];
7160
7161 _cachedSelectedTextRange = nil;
7162 _selectionNeedsUpdate = YES;
7163 // If we are changing the selection with a gesture there is no need
7164 // to wait to paint the selection.
7165 if (_usingGestureForSelection)
7166 [self _updateChangedSelection];
7167
7168#if USE(UIKIT_KEYBOARD_ADDITIONS)
7169 if (_candidateViewNeedsUpdate) {
7170 _candidateViewNeedsUpdate = NO;
7171 if ([self.inputDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(layoutHasChanged)])
7172 [(id <UITextInputDelegatePrivate>)self.inputDelegate layoutHasChanged];
7173 }
7174#endif
7175
7176 [_webView _didChangeEditorState];
7177
7178 if (!_page->editorState().isMissingPostLayoutData) {
7179 _lastInsertedCharacterToOverrideCharacterBeforeSelection = std::nullopt;
7180 if (!_usingGestureForSelection && _focusedElementInformation.autocapitalizeType == WebCore::AutocapitalizeType::Words)
7181 [UIKeyboardImpl.sharedInstance clearShiftState];
7182 }
7183}

7187 [self beginSelectionChange];
7188 _page->extendSelection(WebCore::TextGranularity::WordGranularity, [weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self)] {
7189 if (auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get())
7190 [strongSelf endSelectionChange];
7191 });
7192}

7206- (void)_updateChangedSelection
7207{
7208 [self _updateChangedSelection:NO];
7209}
7210
7211- (void)_updateChangedSelection:(BOOL)force
7212{
7213 auto& editorState = _page->editorState();
7214 if (editorState.isMissingPostLayoutData)
7215 return;
7216
7217 auto& postLayoutData = editorState.postLayoutData();
7218 WebKit::WKSelectionDrawingInfo selectionDrawingInfo { editorState };
7219 if (force || selectionDrawingInfo != _lastSelectionDrawingInfo) {
7220 LOG_WITH_STREAM(Selection, stream << "_updateChangedSelection " << selectionDrawingInfo);
7221
7222 _cachedSelectedTextRange = nil;
7223 _lastSelectionDrawingInfo = selectionDrawingInfo;
7224
7225 // FIXME: We need to figure out what to do if the selection is changed by Javascript.
7226 if (_textInteractionAssistant) {
7227 _markedText = editorState.hasComposition ? postLayoutData.markedText : String { };
7228 [_textInteractionAssistant selectionChanged];
7229 }
7230
7231 _selectionNeedsUpdate = NO;
7232 if (_shouldRestoreSelection) {
7233 [_textInteractionAssistant didEndScrollingOverflow];
7234 _shouldRestoreSelection = NO;
7235 }
7236 }
7237
7238 if (postLayoutData.isStableStateUpdate && _needsDeferredEndScrollingSelectionUpdate && _page->inStableState()) {
7239 [[self selectionInteractionAssistant] showSelectionCommands];
7240
7241 if (!_suppressSelectionAssistantReasons)
7242 [_textInteractionAssistant activateSelection];
7243
7244 [_textInteractionAssistant didEndScrollingOverflow];
7245
7246 _needsDeferredEndScrollingSelectionUpdate = NO;
7247 }
7248}
7249
7250- (BOOL)shouldAllowHidingSelectionCommands
7251{
7252 ASSERT(_ignoreSelectionCommandFadeCount >= 0);
7253 return !_ignoreSelectionCommandFadeCount;
7254}
7255
7256- (BOOL)supportsTextSelectionWithCharacterGranularity
7257{
7258 return YES;
7259}

7261- (BOOL)hasHiddenContentEditable
7262{
7263 return _suppressSelectionAssistantReasons.containsAny({ WebKit::EditableRootIsTransparentOrFullyClipped, WebKit::FocusedElementIsTooSmall });
7264}
7265
7266- (BOOL)_shouldSuppressSelectionCommands
7267{
7268 return !!_suppressSelectionAssistantReasons;
7269}
7270
7271- (void)_startSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:(WebKit::SuppressSelectionAssistantReason)reason
7272{
7273 bool wasSuppressingSelectionAssistant = !!_suppressSelectionAssistantReasons;
7274 _suppressSelectionAssistantReasons.add(reason);
7275
7276 if (!wasSuppressingSelectionAssistant)
7277 [_textInteractionAssistant deactivateSelection];
7278}
7279
7280- (void)_stopSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:(WebKit::SuppressSelectionAssistantReason)reason
7281{
7282 bool wasSuppressingSelectionAssistant = !!_suppressSelectionAssistantReasons;
7283 _suppressSelectionAssistantReasons.remove(reason);
7284
7285 if (wasSuppressingSelectionAssistant && !_suppressSelectionAssistantReasons)
7286 [_textInteractionAssistant activateSelection];
7287}

7325- (void)updateTextSuggestionsForInputDelegate
7326{
7327 // Text suggestions vended from clients take precedence over text suggestions from a focused form control with a datalist.
7328 id <UITextInputSuggestionDelegate> inputDelegate = (id <UITextInputSuggestionDelegate>)self.inputDelegate;
7329 NSArray<UITextSuggestion *> *formInputSessionSuggestions = [_formInputSession suggestions];
7330 if (formInputSessionSuggestions.count) {
7331 [inputDelegate setSuggestions:formInputSessionSuggestions];
7332 return;
7333 }
7334
7335#if ENABLE(DATALIST_ELEMENT)
7336 if ([_dataListTextSuggestions count]) {
7337 [inputDelegate setSuggestions:_dataListTextSuggestions.get()];
7338 return;
7339 }
7340#endif
7341
7342 [inputDelegate setSuggestions:nil];
7343}

7477#pragma mark - UITextInputMultiDocument
7478
7479- (BOOL)_restoreFocusWithToken:(id <NSCopying, NSSecureCoding>)token
7480{
7481 if (_focusStateStack.isEmpty()) {
7482 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
7483 return NO;
7484 }
7485
7486 if (_focusStateStack.takeLast())
7487 [_webView _decrementFocusPreservationCount];
7488
7489 // FIXME: Our current behavior in -_restoreFocusWithToken: does not force the web view to become first responder
7490 // by refocusing the currently focused element. As such, we return NO here so that UIKit will tell WKContentView
7491 // to become first responder in the future.
7492 return NO;
7493}
7494
7495- (void)startRelinquishingFirstResponderToFocusedElement
7496{
7497 if (_isRelinquishingFirstResponderToFocusedElement)
7498 return;
7499
7500 _isRelinquishingFirstResponderToFocusedElement = YES;
7501 [_webView _incrementFocusPreservationCount];
7502}
7503
7504- (void)stopRelinquishingFirstResponderToFocusedElement
7505{
7506 if (!_isRelinquishingFirstResponderToFocusedElement)
7507 return;
7508
7509 _isRelinquishingFirstResponderToFocusedElement = NO;
7510 [_webView _decrementFocusPreservationCount];
7511}

7514{

7516 [_webView _incrementFocusPreservationCount];
7517 _focusStateStack.append(true);
7518 } else
7519 _focusStateStack.append(false);
7520}

7531- (BOOL)gestureRecognizer:(UIGestureRecognizer *)gestureRecognizer isInterruptingMomentumScrollingWithEvent:(UIEvent *)event
7532{
7533 NSSet<UITouch *> *touches = [event touchesForGestureRecognizer:gestureRecognizer];
7534 for (UITouch *touch in touches) {
7535 if ([touch.view isKindOfClass:[UIScrollView class]] && [(UIScrollView *)touch.view _isInterruptingDeceleration])
7536 return YES;
7537 }
7538 return self._scroller._isInterruptingDeceleration;
7539}

7603- (BOOL)actionSheetAssistant:(WKActionSheetAssistant *)assistant showCustomSheetForElement:(_WKActivatedElementInfo *)element
7604{
7605 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = static_cast<id <WKUIDelegatePrivate>>([_webView UIDelegate]);
7606
7607 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:showCustomSheetForElement:)]) {
7608 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
7609 if ([uiDelegate _webView:self.webView showCustomSheetForElement:element]) {
7610#if ENABLE(DRAG_SUPPORT)
7611 BOOL shouldCancelAllTouches = !_dragDropInteractionState.dragSession();
7612#else
7613 BOOL shouldCancelAllTouches = YES;
7614#endif
7615
7616 // Prevent tap-and-hold and panning.
7617 if (shouldCancelAllTouches)
7618 [UIApp _cancelAllTouches];
7619
7620 return YES;
7621 }
7622 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
7623 }
7624
7625 return NO;
7626}

7653- (NSDictionary *)dataDetectionContextForPositionInformation:(const WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition&)positionInformation
7654{
7655 RetainPtr<NSMutableDictionary> context;
7656 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = static_cast<id <WKUIDelegatePrivate>>([_webView UIDelegate]);
7657 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_dataDetectionContextForWebView:)])
7658 context = adoptNS([[uiDelegate _dataDetectionContextForWebView:self.webView] mutableCopy]);
7659
7660 if (!context)
7661 context = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
7662
7663#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
7664 if (!positionInformation.textBefore.isEmpty())
7665 context.get()[getkDataDetectorsLeadingText()] = positionInformation.textBefore;
7666 if (!positionInformation.textAfter.isEmpty())
7667 context.get()[getkDataDetectorsTrailingText()] = positionInformation.textAfter;
7668
7669 CGRect sourceRect;
7670 if (positionInformation.isLink)
7671 sourceRect = positionInformation.linkIndicator.textBoundingRectInRootViewCoordinates;
7672 else if (!positionInformation.dataDetectorBounds.isEmpty())
7673 sourceRect = positionInformation.dataDetectorBounds;
7674 else
7675 sourceRect = positionInformation.bounds;
7676
7677 CGRect frameInContainerViewCoordinates = [self convertRect:sourceRect toView:self.containerForContextMenuHintPreviews];
7678 return [getDDContextMenuActionClass() updateContext:context.get() withSourceRect:frameInContainerViewCoordinates];
7679#else
7680 return context.autorelease();
7681#endif
7682}

7778#if HAVE(PASTEBOARD_DATA_OWNER)
7779
7780static WebCore::DataOwnerType coreDataOwnerType(_UIDataOwner platformType)
7781{
7782 switch (platformType) {
7783 case _UIDataOwnerUser:
7784 return WebCore::DataOwnerType::User;
7785 case _UIDataOwnerEnterprise:
7786 return WebCore::DataOwnerType::Enterprise;
7787 case _UIDataOwnerShared:
7788 return WebCore::DataOwnerType::Shared;
7789 case _UIDataOwnerUndefined:
7790 return WebCore::DataOwnerType::Undefined;
7791 }
7792 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
7793 return WebCore::DataOwnerType::Undefined;
7794}
7795
7796- (WebCore::DataOwnerType)_dataOwnerForPasteboard:(WebKit::PasteboardAccessIntent)intent
7797{
7798 if (![self respondsToSelector:@selector(_dataOwnerForPaste)]) {
7799 // FIXME: Remove this once the relevant bots have fix for <rdar://problem/73852335>.
7800 return WebCore::DataOwnerType::Undefined;
7801 }
7802
7803 if (intent == WebKit::PasteboardAccessIntent::Read)
7804 return coreDataOwnerType(self._dataOwnerForPaste);
7805
7806 if (intent == WebKit::PasteboardAccessIntent::Write)
7807 return coreDataOwnerType(self._dataOwnerForCopy);
7808
7809 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
7810 return WebCore::DataOwnerType::Undefined;
7811}

7894- (void)_updateFrameOfContainerForContextMenuHintPreviewsIfNeeded
7895{
7896 if (!_contextMenuHintContainerView)
7897 return;

7899 CGPoint newOffset = [_scrollViewForTargetedPreview convertPoint:CGPointZero toView:[_contextMenuHintContainerView superview]];
7900

7902 frame.origin.x = newOffset.x - _scrollViewForTargetedPreviewInitialOffset.x;
7903 frame.origin.y = newOffset.y - _scrollViewForTargetedPreviewInitialOffset.y;
7904 [_contextMenuHintContainerView setFrame:frame];
7905}

7907- (void)_updateTargetedPreviewScrollViewUsingContainerScrollingNodeID:(WebCore::ScrollingNodeID)scrollingNodeID
7908{

7911 if (UIScrollView *scrollViewForScrollingNode = scrollingCoordinator->scrollViewForScrollingNodeID(scrollingNodeID))
7912 _scrollViewForTargetedPreview = scrollViewForScrollingNode;
7913 }
7914 }
7915
7916 if (!_scrollViewForTargetedPreview)
7917 _scrollViewForTargetedPreview = self.webView.scrollView;
7918
7919 _scrollViewForTargetedPreviewInitialOffset = [_scrollViewForTargetedPreview convertPoint:CGPointZero toView:[_contextMenuHintContainerView superview]];
7920}

7922#pragma mark - WKDeferringGestureRecognizerDelegate
7923
7924- (WebKit::ShouldDeferGestures)deferringGestureRecognizer:(WKDeferringGestureRecognizer *)deferringGestureRecognizer willBeginTouchesWithEvent:(UIEvent *)event
7925{
7926 self.gestureRecognizerConsistencyEnforcer.beginTracking(deferringGestureRecognizer);
7927
7928 return [self gestureRecognizer:deferringGestureRecognizer isInterruptingMomentumScrollingWithEvent:event] ? WebKit::ShouldDeferGestures::No : WebKit::ShouldDeferGestures::Yes;
7929}
7930
7931- (void)deferringGestureRecognizer:(WKDeferringGestureRecognizer *)deferringGestureRecognizer didTransitionToState:(UIGestureRecognizerState)state
7932{
7933 if (state == UIGestureRecognizerStateEnded || state == UIGestureRecognizerStateFailed || state == UIGestureRecognizerStateCancelled)
7934 self.gestureRecognizerConsistencyEnforcer.endTracking(deferringGestureRecognizer);
7935}
7936
7937- (void)deferringGestureRecognizer:(WKDeferringGestureRecognizer *)deferringGestureRecognizer didEndTouchesWithEvent:(UIEvent *)event
7938{
7939 self.gestureRecognizerConsistencyEnforcer.endTracking(deferringGestureRecognizer);
7940
7941 if (deferringGestureRecognizer.state != UIGestureRecognizerStatePossible)
7942 return;
7943
7944 if (_page->isHandlingPreventableTouchStart() && [self _isTouchStartDeferringGesture:deferringGestureRecognizer])
7945 return;
7946
7947 if (_page->isHandlingPreventableTouchEnd() && [self _isTouchEndDeferringGesture:deferringGestureRecognizer])
7948 return;
7949
7950 if ([_touchEventGestureRecognizer state] == UIGestureRecognizerStatePossible)
7951 return;
7952
7953 // In the case where the touch event gesture recognizer has failed or ended already and we are not in the middle of handling
7954 // an asynchronous (but preventable) touch event, this is our last chance to lift the gesture "gate" by failing the deferring
7955 // gesture recognizer.
7956 deferringGestureRecognizer.state = UIGestureRecognizerStateFailed;
7957}
7958
7959- (BOOL)deferringGestureRecognizer:(WKDeferringGestureRecognizer *)deferringGestureRecognizer shouldDeferOtherGestureRecognizer:(UIGestureRecognizer *)gestureRecognizer
7960{
7961#if ENABLE(IOS_TOUCH_EVENTS)
7962 if ([self _touchEventsMustRequireGestureRecognizerToFail:gestureRecognizer])
7963 return NO;
7964
7965 auto webView = _webView.getAutoreleased();
7966 auto view = gestureRecognizer.view;
7967 BOOL gestureIsInstalledOnOrUnderWebView = NO;
7968 while (view) {
7969 if (view == webView) {
7970 gestureIsInstalledOnOrUnderWebView = YES;
7971 break;
7972 }
7973 view = view.superview;
7974 }
7975
7976 if (!gestureIsInstalledOnOrUnderWebView)
7977 return NO;
7978
7979 if ([gestureRecognizer isKindOfClass:WKDeferringGestureRecognizer.class])
7980 return NO;
7981
7982 if (gestureRecognizer == _touchEventGestureRecognizer)
7983 return NO;
7984
7985#if ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
7986 if (deferringGestureRecognizer == _imageAnalysisDeferringGestureRecognizer)
7987 return [self shouldDeferGestureDueToImageAnalysis:gestureRecognizer];
7988#endif
7989
7990 auto mayDelayResetOfContainingSubgraph = [&](UIGestureRecognizer *gesture) -> BOOL {
7991#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU) && HAVE(LINK_PREVIEW)
7992 if (gesture == [_contextMenuInteraction gestureRecognizerForFailureRelationships])
7993 return YES;
7994#endif
7995
7996#if ENABLE(DRAG_SUPPORT)
7997 if (gesture.delegate == [_dragInteraction _initiationDriver])
7998 return YES;
7999#endif
8000
8001 if (gestureRecognizer._wk_isTapAndAHalf)
8002 return YES;
8003
8004 if (gestureRecognizer == [_textInteractionAssistant loupeGesture])
8005 return YES;
8006
8007 if ([gesture isKindOfClass:UITapGestureRecognizer.class]) {
8008 UITapGestureRecognizer *tapGesture = (UITapGestureRecognizer *)gesture;
8009 return tapGesture.numberOfTapsRequired > 1 && tapGesture.numberOfTouchesRequired < 2;
8010 }
8011
8012 return NO;
8013 };
8014
8015 BOOL isSyntheticTap = [gestureRecognizer isKindOfClass:WKSyntheticTapGestureRecognizer.class];
8016 BOOL mayDelayReset = mayDelayResetOfContainingSubgraph(gestureRecognizer);
8017 if ([gestureRecognizer isKindOfClass:UITapGestureRecognizer.class]) {
8018 if (deferringGestureRecognizer == _touchEndDeferringGestureRecognizerForSyntheticTapGestures)
8019 return isSyntheticTap;
8020
8021 if (deferringGestureRecognizer == _touchEndDeferringGestureRecognizerForDelayedResettableGestures)
8022 return !isSyntheticTap && mayDelayReset;
8023
8024 if (deferringGestureRecognizer == _touchEndDeferringGestureRecognizerForImmediatelyResettableGestures)
8025 return !isSyntheticTap && !mayDelayReset;
8026 }
8027
8028 if (isSyntheticTap)
8029 return deferringGestureRecognizer == _touchStartDeferringGestureRecognizerForSyntheticTapGestures;
8030
8031 if (mayDelayReset)
8032 return deferringGestureRecognizer == _touchStartDeferringGestureRecognizerForDelayedResettableGestures;
8033
8034 return deferringGestureRecognizer == _touchStartDeferringGestureRecognizerForImmediatelyResettableGestures;
8035#else
8036 UNUSED_PARAM(deferringGestureRecognizer);
8037 UNUSED_PARAM(gestureRecognizer);
8038 return NO;
8039#endif
8040}

8042#if ENABLE(DRAG_SUPPORT)
8043
8044static BOOL shouldEnableDragInteractionForPolicy(_WKDragInteractionPolicy policy)
8045{
8046 switch (policy) {
8047 case _WKDragInteractionPolicyAlwaysEnable:
8048 return YES;
8049 case _WKDragInteractionPolicyAlwaysDisable:
8050 return NO;
8051 default:
8052 return [UIDragInteraction isEnabledByDefault];
8053 }
8054}
8055

8059}

8061- (NSTimeInterval)dragLiftDelay
8062{
8063 static const NSTimeInterval mediumDragLiftDelay = 0.5;
8064 static const NSTimeInterval longDragLiftDelay = 0.65;
8065 auto dragLiftDelay = self.webView.configuration._dragLiftDelay;
8066 if (dragLiftDelay == _WKDragLiftDelayMedium)
8067 return mediumDragLiftDelay;
8068 if (dragLiftDelay == _WKDragLiftDelayLong)
8069 return longDragLiftDelay;
8070 return _UIDragInteractionDefaultLiftDelay();
8071}

8076}

8078- (void)setUpDragAndDropInteractions
8079{
8080 _dragInteraction = adoptNS([[UIDragInteraction alloc] initWithDelegate:self]);
8081 _dropInteraction = adoptNS([[UIDropInteraction alloc] initWithDelegate:self]);
8082 [_dragInteraction _setLiftDelay:self.dragLiftDelay];
8083 [_dragInteraction setEnabled:shouldEnableDragInteractionForPolicy(self.webView._dragInteractionPolicy)];
8084#if HAVE(UIKIT_WITH_MOUSE_SUPPORT)
8085 [_dragInteraction _setAllowsPointerDragBeforeLiftDelay:NO];
8086#endif
8087
8088 [self addInteraction:_dragInteraction.get()];
8089 [self addInteraction:_dropInteraction.get()];
8090}
8091
8092- (void)teardownDragAndDropInteractions
8093{
8094 if (_dragInteraction)
8095 [self removeInteraction:_dragInteraction.get()];
8096
8097 if (_dropInteraction)
8098 [self removeInteraction:_dropInteraction.get()];
8099
8100 _dragInteraction = nil;
8101 _dropInteraction = nil;
8102
8103 [self cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
8104}

8106- (void)_startDrag:(RetainPtr<CGImageRef>)image item:(const WebCore::DragItem&)item
8107{
8108 ASSERT(item.sourceAction);
8109
8110 if (item.promisedAttachmentInfo)
8111 [self _prepareToDragPromisedAttachment:item.promisedAttachmentInfo];
8112
8113 auto dragImage = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:image.get() scale:_page->deviceScaleFactor() orientation:UIImageOrientationUp]);
8114 _dragDropInteractionState.stageDragItem(item, dragImage.get());
8115}
8116
8117- (void)_didHandleAdditionalDragItemsRequest:(BOOL)added
8118{
8119 auto completion = _dragDropInteractionState.takeAddDragItemCompletionBlock();
8120 if (!completion)
8121 return;
8122
8123 auto *registrationLists = [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] takeRegistrationLists];
8124 if (!added || ![registrationLists count] || !_dragDropInteractionState.hasStagedDragSource()) {
8125 _dragDropInteractionState.clearStagedDragSource();
8126 completion(@[ ]);
8127 return;
8128 }
8129
8130 auto stagedDragSource = _dragDropInteractionState.stagedDragSource();
8131 NSArray *dragItemsToAdd = [self _itemsForBeginningOrAddingToSessionWithRegistrationLists:registrationLists stagedDragSource:stagedDragSource];
8132
8133 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session: %p adding %tu items", _dragDropInteractionState.dragSession(), dragItemsToAdd.count);
8134 _dragDropInteractionState.clearStagedDragSource(dragItemsToAdd.count ? WebKit::DragDropInteractionState::DidBecomeActive::Yes : WebKit::DragDropInteractionState::DidBecomeActive::No);
8135
8136 completion(dragItemsToAdd);
8137
8138 if (dragItemsToAdd.count)
8139 _page->didStartDrag();
8140}
8141
8142- (void)_didHandleDragStartRequest:(BOOL)started
8143{
8144 BlockPtr<void()> savedCompletionBlock = _dragDropInteractionState.takeDragStartCompletionBlock();
8145 ASSERT(savedCompletionBlock);
8146
8147 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Handling drag start request (started: %d, completion block: %p)", started, savedCompletionBlock.get());
8148 if (savedCompletionBlock)
8149 savedCompletionBlock();
8150
8151 if (!_dragDropInteractionState.dragSession().items.count) {
8152 auto positionForDragEnd = WebCore::roundedIntPoint(_dragDropInteractionState.adjustedPositionForDragEnd());
8153 [self cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
8154 if (started) {
8155 // A client of the Objective C SPI or UIKit might have prevented the drag from beginning entirely in the UI process, in which case
8156 // we need to balance the `dragstart` event with a `dragend`.
8157 _page->dragEnded(positionForDragEnd, positionForDragEnd, { });
8158 }
8159 }
8160}
8161
8162- (void)computeClientAndGlobalPointsForDropSession:(id <UIDropSession>)session outClientPoint:(CGPoint *)outClientPoint outGlobalPoint:(CGPoint *)outGlobalPoint
8163{
8164 // FIXME: This makes the behavior of drag events on iOS consistent with other synthetic mouse events on iOS (see WebPage::completeSyntheticClick).
8165 // However, we should experiment with making the client position relative to the window and the global position in document coordinates. See
8166 // https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=173855 for more details.
8167 auto locationInContentView = [session locationInView:self];
8168 if (outClientPoint)
8169 *outClientPoint = locationInContentView;
8170
8171 if (outGlobalPoint)
8172 *outGlobalPoint = locationInContentView;
8173}
8174
8175static UIDropOperation dropOperationForWebCoreDragOperation(std::optional<WebCore::DragOperation> operation)
8176{
8177 if (operation) {
8178 if (*operation == WebCore::DragOperation::Move)
8179 return UIDropOperationMove;
8180 if (*operation == WebCore::DragOperation::Copy)
8181 return UIDropOperationCopy;
8182 }
8183 return UIDropOperationCancel;
8184}
8185
8186static std::optional<WebCore::DragOperation> coreDragOperationForUIDropOperation(UIDropOperation dropOperation)
8187{
8188 switch (dropOperation) {
8189 case UIDropOperationCancel:
8190 return std::nullopt;
8191 case UIDropOperationForbidden:
8192 return WebCore::DragOperation::Private;
8193 case UIDropOperationCopy:
8194 return WebCore::DragOperation::Copy;
8195 case UIDropOperationMove:
8196 return WebCore::DragOperation::Move;
8197 }
8198 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
8199 return std::nullopt;
8200}
8201
8202- (WebCore::DragData)dragDataForDropSession:(id <UIDropSession>)session dragDestinationAction:(WKDragDestinationAction)dragDestinationAction
8203{
8204 CGPoint global;
8205 CGPoint client;
8206 [self computeClientAndGlobalPointsForDropSession:session outClientPoint:&client outGlobalPoint:&global];
8207
8208 auto dragOperationMask = WebCore::anyDragOperation();
8209 if (!session.allowsMoveOperation)
8210 dragOperationMask.remove(WebCore::DragOperation::Move);
8211
8212 return {
8213 session,
8214 WebCore::roundedIntPoint(client),
8215 WebCore::roundedIntPoint(global),
8216 dragOperationMask,
8217 { },
8218 WebKit::coreDragDestinationActionMask(dragDestinationAction),
8219 _page->webPageID()
8220 };
8221}
8222
8223- (void)cleanUpDragSourceSessionState
8224{
8225 if (_waitingForEditDragSnapshot)
8226 return;
8227
8228 if (_dragDropInteractionState.dragSession() || _dragDropInteractionState.isPerformingDrop())
8229 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Cleaning up dragging state (has pending operation: %d)", [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] hasPendingOperation]);
8230
8231 if (![[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] hasPendingOperation]) {
8232 // If we're performing a drag operation, don't clear out the pasteboard yet, since another web view may still require access to it.
8233 // The pasteboard will be cleared after the last client is finished performing a drag operation using the item providers.
8234 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] setItemProviders:nil];
8235 }
8236
8237 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] clearRegistrationLists];
8238 [self _restoreCalloutBarIfNeeded];
8239
8240 [self _removeContainerForDragPreviews];
8241 [std::exchange(_visibleContentViewSnapshot, nil) removeFromSuperview];
8242 [_editDropCaretView remove];
8243 _editDropCaretView = nil;
8244 _shouldRestoreCalloutBarAfterDrop = NO;
8245
8246 _dragDropInteractionState.dragAndDropSessionsDidEnd();
8247 _dragDropInteractionState = { };
8248}
8249
8250static NSArray<NSItemProvider *> *extractItemProvidersFromDragItems(NSArray<UIDragItem *> *dragItems)
8251{
8252 NSMutableArray<NSItemProvider *> *providers = [NSMutableArray array];
8253 for (UIDragItem *item in dragItems) {
8254 if (NSItemProvider *provider = item.itemProvider)
8255 [providers addObject:provider];
8256 }
8257 return providers;
8258}
8259
8260static NSArray<NSItemProvider *> *extractItemProvidersFromDropSession(id <UIDropSession> session)
8261{
8262 return extractItemProvidersFromDragItems(session.items);
8263}

8265- (void)_willReceiveEditDragSnapshot
8266{
8267 _waitingForEditDragSnapshot = YES;
8268}
8269
8270- (void)_didReceiveEditDragSnapshot:(std::optional<WebCore::TextIndicatorData>)data
8271{
8272 _waitingForEditDragSnapshot = NO;
8273
8274 [self _deliverDelayedDropPreviewIfPossible:data];
8275 [self cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
8276
8277 if (auto action = WTFMove(_actionToPerformAfterReceivingEditDragSnapshot))
8278 action();
8279}

8281- (void)_deliverDelayedDropPreviewIfPossible:(std::optional<WebCore::TextIndicatorData>)data
8282{
8283 if (!_visibleContentViewSnapshot)
8284 return;
8285
8286 if (!data)
8287 return;
8288
8289 if (!data->contentImage)
8290 return;
8291
8292 auto snapshotWithoutSelection = data->contentImageWithoutSelection;
8293 if (!snapshotWithoutSelection)
8294 return;
8295
8296 auto unselectedSnapshotImage = snapshotWithoutSelection->nativeImage();
8297 if (!unselectedSnapshotImage)
8298 return;
8299
8300 if (!_dropAnimationCount)
8301 return;
8302
8303 auto unselectedContentImageForEditDrag = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:unselectedSnapshotImage->platformImage().get() scale:_page->deviceScaleFactor() orientation:UIImageOrientationUp]);
8304 _unselectedContentSnapshot = adoptNS([[UIImageView alloc] initWithImage:unselectedContentImageForEditDrag.get()]);
8305 [_unselectedContentSnapshot setFrame:data->contentImageWithoutSelectionRectInRootViewCoordinates];
8306
8307 [self insertSubview:_unselectedContentSnapshot.get() belowSubview:_visibleContentViewSnapshot.get()];
8308 _dragDropInteractionState.deliverDelayedDropPreview(self, self.containerForDropPreviews, data.value());
8309}
8310
8311- (void)_didPerformDragOperation:(BOOL)handled
8312{
8313 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Finished performing drag controller operation (handled: %d)", handled);
8314 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] decrementPendingOperationCount];
8315 id <UIDropSession> dropSession = _dragDropInteractionState.dropSession();
8316 if ([self.webViewUIDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:dataInteractionOperationWasHandled:forSession:itemProviders:)])
8317 [self.webViewUIDelegate _webView:self.webView dataInteractionOperationWasHandled:handled forSession:dropSession itemProviders:[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance].itemProviders];
8318
8319 CGPoint global;
8320 CGPoint client;
8321 [self computeClientAndGlobalPointsForDropSession:dropSession outClientPoint:&client outGlobalPoint:&global];
8322 [self cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
8323 auto currentDragOperation = _page->currentDragOperation();
8324 _page->dragEnded(WebCore::roundedIntPoint(client), WebCore::roundedIntPoint(global), currentDragOperation ? *currentDragOperation : OptionSet<WebCore::DragOperation>({ }));
8325}
8326
8327- (void)_didChangeDragCaretRect:(CGRect)previousRect currentRect:(CGRect)rect
8328{
8329 BOOL previousRectIsEmpty = CGRectIsEmpty(previousRect);
8330 BOOL currentRectIsEmpty = CGRectIsEmpty(rect);
8331 if (previousRectIsEmpty && currentRectIsEmpty)
8332 return;
8333
8334 if (previousRectIsEmpty) {
8335 _editDropCaretView = adoptNS([[_UITextDragCaretView alloc] initWithTextInputView:self]);
8336 [_editDropCaretView insertAtPosition:[WKTextPosition textPositionWithRect:rect]];
8337 return;
8338 }
8339
8340 if (currentRectIsEmpty) {
8341 [_editDropCaretView remove];
8342 _editDropCaretView = nil;
8343 return;
8344 }
8345
8346 [_editDropCaretView updateToPosition:[WKTextPosition textPositionWithRect:rect]];
8347}
8348
8349- (void)_prepareToDragPromisedAttachment:(const WebCore::PromisedAttachmentInfo&)info
8350{
8351 auto session = retainPtr(_dragDropInteractionState.dragSession());
8352 if (!session) {
8353 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
8354 return;
8355 }
8356
8357 auto numberOfAdditionalTypes = info.additionalTypes.size();
8358 ASSERT(numberOfAdditionalTypes == info.additionalData.size());
8359
8360 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session: %p preparing to drag with attachment identifier: %s", session.get(), info.attachmentIdentifier.utf8().data());
8361
8362 NSString *utiType = nil;
8363 NSString *fileName = nil;
8364 if (auto attachment = _page->attachmentForIdentifier(info.attachmentIdentifier)) {
8365 utiType = attachment->utiType();
8366 fileName = attachment->fileName();
8367 }
8368
8369 auto registrationList = adoptNS([[WebItemProviderRegistrationInfoList alloc] init]);
8370 [registrationList setPreferredPresentationStyle:WebPreferredPresentationStyleAttachment];
8371 if ([fileName length])
8372 [registrationList setSuggestedName:fileName];
8373 if (numberOfAdditionalTypes == info.additionalData.size() && numberOfAdditionalTypes) {
8374 for (size_t index = 0; index < numberOfAdditionalTypes; ++index) {
8375 auto nsData = info.additionalData[index]->createNSData();
8376 [registrationList addData:nsData.get() forType:info.additionalTypes[index]];
8377 }
8378 }
8379
8380 [registrationList addPromisedType:utiType fileCallback:[session = WTFMove(session), weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self), info] (WebItemProviderFileCallback callback) {
8381 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
8382 if (!strongSelf) {
8383 callback(nil, [NSError errorWithDomain:WKErrorDomain code:WKErrorWebViewInvalidated userInfo:nil]);
8384 return;
8385 }
8386
8387 NSString *temporaryBlobDirectory = FileSystem::createTemporaryDirectory(@"blobs");
8388 NSURL *destinationURL = [NSURL fileURLWithPath:[temporaryBlobDirectory stringByAppendingPathComponent:[NSUUID UUID].UUIDString] isDirectory:NO];
8389
8390 auto attachment = strongSelf->_page->attachmentForIdentifier(info.attachmentIdentifier);
8391 if (attachment && attachment->fileWrapper()) {
8392 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session: %p delivering promised attachment: %s at path: %@", session.get(), info.attachmentIdentifier.utf8().data(), destinationURL.path);
8393 NSError *fileWrapperError = nil;
8394 if ([attachment->fileWrapper() writeToURL:destinationURL options:0 originalContentsURL:nil error:&fileWrapperError])
8395 callback(destinationURL, nil);
8396 else
8397 callback(nil, fileWrapperError);
8398 } else
8399 callback(nil, [NSError errorWithDomain:WKErrorDomain code:WKErrorWebViewInvalidated userInfo:nil]);
8400
8401 [ensureLocalDragSessionContext(session.get()) addTemporaryDirectory:temporaryBlobDirectory];
8402 }];
8403
8404 WebItemProviderPasteboard *pasteboard = [WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance];
8405 pasteboard.itemProviders = @[ [registrationList itemProvider] ];
8406 [pasteboard stageRegistrationLists:@[ registrationList.get() ]];
8407}
8408
8409- (WKDragDestinationAction)_dragDestinationActionForDropSession:(id <UIDropSession>)session
8410{
8411 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = self.webViewUIDelegate;
8412 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:dragDestinationActionMaskForDraggingInfo:)])
8413 return [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView dragDestinationActionMaskForDraggingInfo:session];
8414
8415 return WKDragDestinationActionAny & ~WKDragDestinationActionLoad;
8416}

8418- (OptionSet<WebCore::DragSourceAction>)_allowedDragSourceActions
8419{
8420 auto allowedActions = WebCore::anyDragSourceAction();
8421 if (!self.isFirstResponder || !_suppressSelectionAssistantReasons.isEmpty()) {
8422 // Don't allow starting a drag on a selection when selection views are not visible.
8423 allowedActions.remove(WebCore::DragSourceAction::Selection);
8424 }
8425 return allowedActions;
8426}

8435- (void)_restoreCalloutBarIfNeeded
8436{
8437 if (!_shouldRestoreCalloutBarAfterDrop)
8438 return;
8439
8440 // FIXME: This SPI should be renamed in UIKit to reflect a more general purpose of revealing hidden interaction assistant controls.
8441 [_textInteractionAssistant didEndScrollingOverflow];
8442 _shouldRestoreCalloutBarAfterDrop = NO;
8443}
8444
8445- (NSArray<UIDragItem *> *)_itemsForBeginningOrAddingToSessionWithRegistrationLists:(NSArray<WebItemProviderRegistrationInfoList *> *)registrationLists stagedDragSource:(const WebKit::DragSourceState&)stagedDragSource
8446{
8447 if (!registrationLists.count)
8448 return @[ ];
8449
8450 NSMutableArray *adjustedItemProviders = [NSMutableArray array];
8451 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = self.webViewUIDelegate;
8452 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:adjustedDataInteractionItemProvidersForItemProvider:representingObjects:additionalData:)]) {
8453 // FIXME: We should consider a new UI delegate hook that accepts a list of item providers, so we don't need to invoke this delegate method repeatedly for multiple items.
8454 for (WebItemProviderRegistrationInfoList *list in registrationLists) {
8455 NSItemProvider *defaultItemProvider = list.itemProvider;
8456 if (!defaultItemProvider)
8457 continue;
8458
8459 auto representingObjects = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
8460 auto additionalData = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
8461 [list enumerateItems:[representingObjects, additionalData] (id <WebItemProviderRegistrar> item, NSUInteger) {
8462 if ([item respondsToSelector:@selector(representingObjectForClient)])
8463 [representingObjects addObject:item.representingObjectForClient];
8464 if ([item respondsToSelector:@selector(typeIdentifierForClient)] && [item respondsToSelector:@selector(dataForClient)])
8465 [additionalData setObject:item.dataForClient forKey:item.typeIdentifierForClient];
8466 }];
8467 NSArray *adjustedItems = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView adjustedDataInteractionItemProvidersForItemProvider:defaultItemProvider representingObjects:representingObjects.get() additionalData:additionalData.get()];
8468 if (adjustedItems.count)
8469 [adjustedItemProviders addObjectsFromArray:adjustedItems];
8470 }
8471 } else {
8472 for (WebItemProviderRegistrationInfoList *list in registrationLists) {
8473 if (auto *defaultItemProvider = list.itemProvider)
8474 [adjustedItemProviders addObject:defaultItemProvider];
8475 }
8476 }
8477
8478 NSMutableArray *dragItems = [NSMutableArray arrayWithCapacity:adjustedItemProviders.count];
8479 for (NSItemProvider *itemProvider in adjustedItemProviders) {
8480 auto item = adoptNS([[UIDragItem alloc] initWithItemProvider:itemProvider]);
8481 [item _setPrivateLocalContext:@(stagedDragSource.itemIdentifier)];
8482 [dragItems addObject:item.get()];
8483 }
8484
8485 return dragItems;
8486}

8490 [[_textInteractionAssistant loupeGesture] _wk_cancel];
8491 [[_textInteractionAssistant forcePressGesture] _wk_cancel];
8492}

8499- (NSDictionary *)_autofillContext
8500{
8501 if (!self._hasFocusedElement)
8502 return nil;
8503
8504 auto context = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
8505 context.get()[@"_WKAutofillContextVersion"] = @(2);
8506
8507 if (_focusRequiresStrongPasswordAssistance && _focusedElementInformation.elementType == WebKit::InputType::Password) {
8508 context.get()[@"_automaticPasswordKeyboard"] = @YES;
8509 context.get()[@"strongPasswordAdditionalContext"] = _additionalContextForStrongPasswordAssistance.get();
8510 } else if (_focusedElementInformation.acceptsAutofilledLoginCredentials)
8511 context.get()[@"_acceptsLoginCredentials"] = @YES;
8512
8513 NSURL *platformURL = _focusedElementInformation.representingPageURL;
8514 if (platformURL)
8515 context.get()[@"_WebViewURL"] = platformURL;
8516
8517 return context.autorelease();
8518}

8537
8538// FIXME: This should be merged with createTargetedDragPreview in DragDropInteractionState.
8539static RetainPtr<UITargetedPreview> createTargetedPreview(UIImage *image, UIView *rootView, UIView *previewContainer, const WebCore::FloatRect& frameInRootViewCoordinates, const Vector<WebCore::FloatRect>& clippingRectsInFrameCoordinates, UIColor *backgroundColor)
8540{
8541 if (frameInRootViewCoordinates.isEmpty() || !image || !previewContainer.window)
8542 return nil;
8543
8544 WebCore::FloatRect frameInContainerCoordinates = [rootView convertRect:frameInRootViewCoordinates toView:previewContainer];
8545 if (frameInContainerCoordinates.isEmpty())
8546 return nil;
8547
8548 auto scalingRatio = frameInContainerCoordinates.size() / frameInRootViewCoordinates.size();
8549 auto clippingRectValuesInFrameCoordinates = createNSArray(clippingRectsInFrameCoordinates, [&] (WebCore::FloatRect rect) {
8550 rect.scale(scalingRatio);
8551 return [NSValue valueWithCGRect:rect];
8552 });
8553
8554 RetainPtr<UIPreviewParameters> parameters;
8555 if ([clippingRectValuesInFrameCoordinates count])
8556 parameters = adoptNS([[UIPreviewParameters alloc] initWithTextLineRects:clippingRectValuesInFrameCoordinates.get()]);
8557 else
8558 parameters = adoptNS([[UIPreviewParameters alloc] init]);
8559
8560 [parameters setBackgroundColor:(backgroundColor ?: [UIColor clearColor])];
8561
8562 CGPoint centerInContainerCoordinates = { CGRectGetMidX(frameInContainerCoordinates), CGRectGetMidY(frameInContainerCoordinates) };
8563 auto target = adoptNS([[UIPreviewTarget alloc] initWithContainer:previewContainer center:centerInContainerCoordinates]);
8564
8565 auto imageView = adoptNS([[UIImageView alloc] initWithImage:image]);
8566 [imageView setFrame:frameInContainerCoordinates];
8567 return adoptNS([[UITargetedPreview alloc] initWithView:imageView.get() parameters:parameters.get() target:target.get()]);
8568}
8569
8570static RetainPtr<UITargetedPreview> createFallbackTargetedPreview(UIView *rootView, UIView *containerView, const WebCore::FloatRect& frameInRootViewCoordinates, UIColor *backgroundColor)
8571{
8572 if (!containerView.window)
8573 return nil;
8574
8575 if (frameInRootViewCoordinates.isEmpty())
8576 return nil;
8577
8578 auto parameters = adoptNS([[UIPreviewParameters alloc] init]);
8579 if (backgroundColor)
8580 [parameters setBackgroundColor:backgroundColor];
8581
8582 UIView *snapshotView = [rootView resizableSnapshotViewFromRect:frameInRootViewCoordinates afterScreenUpdates:NO withCapInsets:UIEdgeInsetsZero];
8583
8584 CGRect frameInContainerViewCoordinates = [rootView convertRect:frameInRootViewCoordinates toView:containerView];
8585
8586 if (CGRectIsEmpty(frameInContainerViewCoordinates))
8587 return nil;
8588
8589 snapshotView.frame = frameInContainerViewCoordinates;
8590
8591 CGPoint centerInContainerViewCoordinates = CGPointMake(CGRectGetMidX(frameInContainerViewCoordinates), CGRectGetMidY(frameInContainerViewCoordinates));
8592 auto target = adoptNS([[UIPreviewTarget alloc] initWithContainer:containerView center:centerInContainerViewCoordinates]);
8593
8594 return adoptNS([[UITargetedPreview alloc] initWithView:snapshotView parameters:parameters.get() target:target.get()]);
8595}

8597- (UITargetedPreview *)_createTargetedContextMenuHintPreviewForFocusedElement
8598{
8599 auto backgroundColor = [&]() -> UIColor * {
8600 switch (_focusedElementInformation.elementType) {
8601 case WebKit::InputType::Date:
8602 case WebKit::InputType::Month:
8603 case WebKit::InputType::DateTimeLocal:
8604 case WebKit::InputType::Time:
8605 return UIColor.clearColor;
8606 default:
8607 return nil;
8608 }
8609 }();
8610
8611 auto targetedPreview = createFallbackTargetedPreview(self, self.containerForContextMenuHintPreviews, _focusedElementInformation.interactionRect, backgroundColor);
8612
8613 [self _updateTargetedPreviewScrollViewUsingContainerScrollingNodeID:_focusedElementInformation.containerScrollingNodeID];
8614
8615 _contextMenuInteractionTargetedPreview = WTFMove(targetedPreview);
8616 return _contextMenuInteractionTargetedPreview.get();
8617}

8624- (UITargetedPreview *)_createTargetedContextMenuHintPreviewIfPossible
8625{
8626 RetainPtr<UITargetedPreview> targetedPreview;
8627
8628 if (_positionInformation.isLink && _positionInformation.linkIndicator.contentImage) {
8629 auto indicator = _positionInformation.linkIndicator;
8630 auto textIndicatorImage = uiImageForImage(indicator.contentImage.get());
8631 targetedPreview = createTargetedPreview(textIndicatorImage.get(), self, self.containerForContextMenuHintPreviews, indicator.textBoundingRectInRootViewCoordinates, indicator.textRectsInBoundingRectCoordinates, [UIColor colorWithCGColor:cachedCGColor(indicator.estimatedBackgroundColor)]);
8632 } else if ((_positionInformation.isAttachment || _positionInformation.isImage) && _positionInformation.image) {
8633 auto cgImage = _positionInformation.image->makeCGImageCopy();
8634 auto image = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage.get()]);
8635 targetedPreview = createTargetedPreview(image.get(), self, self.containerForContextMenuHintPreviews, _positionInformation.bounds, { }, nil);
8636 }
8637
8638 if (!targetedPreview) {
8639 auto boundsForFallbackPreview = self.positionInformationHasImageOverlayDataDetector ? _positionInformation.dataDetectorBounds : _positionInformation.bounds;
8640 targetedPreview = createFallbackTargetedPreview(self, self.containerForContextMenuHintPreviews, boundsForFallbackPreview, nil);
8641 }
8642
8643 [self _updateTargetedPreviewScrollViewUsingContainerScrollingNodeID:_positionInformation.containerScrollingNodeID];
8644
8645 _contextMenuInteractionTargetedPreview = WTFMove(targetedPreview);
8646 return _contextMenuInteractionTargetedPreview.get();
8647}

8649- (void)_removeContextMenuViewIfPossible
8650{
8651#if HAVE(LINK_PREVIEW)
8652 // If a new _contextMenuElementInfo is installed, we've started another interaction,
8653 // and removing the hint container view will cause the animation to break.
8654 if (_contextMenuElementInfo)
8655 return;
8656#endif
8657#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
8658 // We are also using this container for the action sheet assistant...
8659 if ([_actionSheetAssistant hasContextMenuInteraction])
8660 return;
8661#endif
8662 // and for the file upload panel...
8663 if (_fileUploadPanel)
8664 return;
8665
8666 // and for the date/time picker.
8667 if ([self dateTimeInputControl])
8668 return;
8669
8670 if ([self selectControl])
8671 return;
8672
8673 [self _removeContainerForContextMenuHintPreviews];
8674}

8678#if HAVE(UI_WK_DOCUMENT_CONTEXT)
8679
8680static inline OptionSet<WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options> toWebDocumentRequestOptions(UIWKDocumentRequestFlags flags)
8681{
8682 OptionSet<WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options> options;
8683
8684 if (flags & UIWKDocumentRequestText)
8685 options.add(WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options::Text);
8686 if (flags & UIWKDocumentRequestAttributed)
8687 options.add(WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options::AttributedText);
8688 if (flags & UIWKDocumentRequestRects)
8689 options.add(WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options::Rects);
8690 if (flags & UIWKDocumentRequestSpatial)
8691 options.add(WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options::Spatial);
8692 if (flags & UIWKDocumentRequestAnnotation)
8693 options.add(WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options::Annotation);
8694 if (flags & UIWKDocumentRequestMarkedTextRects)
8695 options.add(WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options::MarkedTextRects);
8696 if (flags & UIWKDocumentRequestSpatialAndCurrentSelection)
8697 options.add(WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest::Options::SpatialAndCurrentSelection);
8698
8699 return options;
8700}
8701
8702static WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest toWebRequest(UIWKDocumentRequest *request)
8703{
8704 WebKit::DocumentEditingContextRequest webRequest = {
8705 .options = toWebDocumentRequestOptions(request.flags),
8706 .surroundingGranularity = toWKTextGranularity(request.surroundingGranularity),
8707 .granularityCount = request.granularityCount,
8708 .rect = request.documentRect
8709 };
8710
8711 if (auto textInputContext = dynamic_objc_cast<_WKTextInputContext>(request.inputElementIdentifier))
8712 webRequest.textInputContext = [textInputContext _textInputContext];
8713
8714 return webRequest;
8715}

8720 _page->updateSelectionWithDelta(static_cast<int64_t>(deltaRange.location), static_cast<int64_t>(deltaRange.length), [capturedCompletionHandler = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler)] {
8721 capturedCompletionHandler();
8722 });
8723}

8746- (void)insertTextPlaceholderWithSize:(CGSize)size completionHandler:(void (^)(UITextPlaceholder *))completionHandler
8747{
8748 _page->insertTextPlaceholder(WebCore::IntSize { size }, [weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self), completionHandler = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler)](const std::optional<WebCore::ElementContext>& placeholder) {

8768
8769static Vector<WebCore::IntSize> sizesOfPlaceholderElementsToInsertWhenDroppingItems(NSArray<NSItemProvider *> *itemProviders)
8770{
8771 Vector<WebCore::IntSize> sizes;
8772 for (NSItemProvider *item in itemProviders) {
8773 if (!WebCore::MIMETypeRegistry::isSupportedImageMIMEType(WebCore::MIMETypeFromUTI(item.web_fileUploadContentTypes.firstObject)))
8774 return { };
8775
8776 WebCore::IntSize presentationSize(item.preferredPresentationSize);
8777 if (presentationSize.isEmpty())
8778 return { };
8779
8780 sizes.append(WTFMove(presentationSize));
8781 }
8782 return sizes;
8783}
8784
8785- (BOOL)_handleDropByInsertingImagePlaceholders:(NSArray<NSItemProvider *> *)itemProviders session:(id <UIDropSession>)session
8786{
8787 if (!self.webView._editable)
8788 return NO;
8789
8790 if (_dragDropInteractionState.dragSession())
8791 return NO;
8792
8793 if (session.items.count != itemProviders.count)
8794 return NO;
8795
8796 auto imagePlaceholderSizes = sizesOfPlaceholderElementsToInsertWhenDroppingItems(itemProviders);
8797 if (imagePlaceholderSizes.isEmpty())
8798 return NO;
8799
8800 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Inserting dropped image placeholders for session: %p", session);
8801
8802 _page->insertDroppedImagePlaceholders(imagePlaceholderSizes, [protectedSelf = retainPtr(self), dragItems = retainPtr(session.items)] (auto& placeholderRects, auto data) {
8803 auto& state = protectedSelf->_dragDropInteractionState;
8804 if (!data || !protectedSelf->_dropAnimationCount) {
8805 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Failed to animate image placeholders: missing text indicator data.");
8806 state.clearAllDelayedItemPreviewProviders();
8807 return;
8808 }
8809
8810 auto snapshotWithoutSelection = data->contentImageWithoutSelection;
8811 if (!snapshotWithoutSelection) {
8812 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Failed to animate image placeholders: missing unselected content image.");
8813 state.clearAllDelayedItemPreviewProviders();
8814 return;
8815 }
8816
8817 auto unselectedSnapshotImage = snapshotWithoutSelection->nativeImage();
8818 if (!unselectedSnapshotImage) {
8819 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Failed to animate image placeholders: could not decode unselected content image.");
8820 state.clearAllDelayedItemPreviewProviders();
8821 return;
8822 }
8823
8824 auto unselectedContentImageForEditDrag = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:unselectedSnapshotImage->platformImage().get() scale:protectedSelf->_page->deviceScaleFactor() orientation:UIImageOrientationUp]);
8825 auto snapshotView = adoptNS([[UIImageView alloc] initWithImage:unselectedContentImageForEditDrag.get()]);
8826 [snapshotView setFrame:data->contentImageWithoutSelectionRectInRootViewCoordinates];
8827 [protectedSelf addSubview:snapshotView.get()];
8828 protectedSelf->_unselectedContentSnapshot = WTFMove(snapshotView);
8829 state.deliverDelayedDropPreview(protectedSelf.get(), [protectedSelf unobscuredContentRect], dragItems.get(), placeholderRects);
8830 });
8831
8832 return YES;
8833}

8835#pragma mark - UIDragInteractionDelegate
8836
8837- (BOOL)_dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction shouldDelayCompetingGestureRecognizer:(UIGestureRecognizer *)competingGestureRecognizer
8838{
8839 if (_highlightLongPressGestureRecognizer == competingGestureRecognizer) {
8840 // Since 3D touch still recognizes alongside the drag lift, and also requires the highlight long press
8841 // gesture to be active to support cancelling when `touchstart` is prevented, we should also allow the
8842 // highlight long press to recognize simultaneously, and manually cancel it when the drag lift is
8843 // recognized (see _dragInteraction:prepareForSession:completion:).
8844 return NO;
8845 }
8846 return [competingGestureRecognizer isKindOfClass:[UILongPressGestureRecognizer class]];
8847}

8858- (void)_dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction itemsForAddingToSession:(id <UIDragSession>)session withTouchAtPoint:(CGPoint)point completion:(void(^)(NSArray<UIDragItem *> *))completion
8859{
8860 if (!_dragDropInteractionState.shouldRequestAdditionalItemForDragSession(session)) {
8861 completion(@[ ]);
8862 return;
8863 }
8864
8865 _dragDropInteractionState.dragSessionWillRequestAdditionalItem(completion);
8866 _page->requestAdditionalItemsForDragSession(WebCore::roundedIntPoint(point), WebCore::roundedIntPoint(point), self._allowedDragSourceActions);
8867}
8868
8869- (void)_dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction prepareForSession:(id <UIDragSession>)session completion:(dispatch_block_t)completion
8870{
8871 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Preparing for drag session: %p", session);
8872 if (self.currentDragOrDropSession) {
8873 // FIXME: Support multiple simultaneous drag sessions in the future.
8874 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session failed: %p (a current drag session already exists)", session);
8875 completion();
8876 return;
8877 }
8878
8879 [self cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
8880
8881 auto prepareForSession = [weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self), session = retainPtr(session), completion = makeBlockPtr(completion)] (WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage) {
8882 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
8883 if (!strongSelf || ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage == WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::Yes)
8884 return;
8885
8886 auto dragOrigin = [session locationInView:strongSelf.get()];
8887 strongSelf->_dragDropInteractionState.prepareForDragSession(session.get(), completion.get());
8888 strongSelf->_page->requestDragStart(WebCore::roundedIntPoint(dragOrigin), WebCore::roundedIntPoint([strongSelf convertPoint:dragOrigin toView:[strongSelf window]]), [strongSelf _allowedDragSourceActions]);
8889 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session requested: %p at origin: {%.0f, %.0f}", session.get(), dragOrigin.x, dragOrigin.y);
8890 };
8891
8892#if ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
8893 [self _doAfterPendingImageAnalysis:prepareForSession];
8894#else
8895 prepareForSession(WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No);
8896#endif
8897}
8898
8899- (NSArray<UIDragItem *> *)dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction itemsForBeginningSession:(id <UIDragSession>)session
8900{
8901 ASSERT(interaction == _dragInteraction);
8902 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag items requested for session: %p", session);
8903 if (_dragDropInteractionState.dragSession() != session) {
8904 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session failed: %p (delegate session does not match %p)", session, _dragDropInteractionState.dragSession());
8905 return @[ ];
8906 }
8907
8908 if (!_dragDropInteractionState.hasStagedDragSource()) {
8909 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session failed: %p (missing staged drag source)", session);
8910 return @[ ];
8911 }
8912
8913 auto stagedDragSource = _dragDropInteractionState.stagedDragSource();
8914 auto *registrationLists = [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] takeRegistrationLists];
8915 NSArray *dragItems = [self _itemsForBeginningOrAddingToSessionWithRegistrationLists:registrationLists stagedDragSource:stagedDragSource];
8916 if (![dragItems count])
8917 _page->dragCancelled();
8918 else
8919 [self _cancelLongPressGestureRecognizer];
8920
8921 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session: %p starting with %tu items", session, [dragItems count]);
8922 _dragDropInteractionState.clearStagedDragSource([dragItems count] ? WebKit::DragDropInteractionState::DidBecomeActive::Yes : WebKit::DragDropInteractionState::DidBecomeActive::No);
8923
8924 return dragItems;
8925}

8927- (UITargetedDragPreview *)dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction previewForLiftingItem:(UIDragItem *)item session:(id <UIDragSession>)session
8928{
8929 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = self.webViewUIDelegate;
8930 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewForLiftingItem:session:)]) {
8931 UITargetedDragPreview *overriddenPreview = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewForLiftingItem:item session:session];
8932 if (overriddenPreview)
8933 return overriddenPreview;
8934 }
8935 return _dragDropInteractionState.previewForDragItem(item, self, self.containerForDragPreviews);
8936}
8937
8938- (void)dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction willAnimateLiftWithAnimator:(id <UIDragAnimating>)animator session:(id <UIDragSession>)session
8939{
8940 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session willAnimateLiftWithAnimator: %p", session);
8941 if (_dragDropInteractionState.anyActiveDragSourceIs(WebCore::DragSourceAction::Selection)) {
8942 [self cancelActiveTextInteractionGestures];
8943 if (!_shouldRestoreCalloutBarAfterDrop) {
8944 // FIXME: This SPI should be renamed in UIKit to reflect a more general purpose of hiding interaction assistant controls.
8945 [_textInteractionAssistant willStartScrollingOverflow];
8946 _shouldRestoreCalloutBarAfterDrop = YES;
8947 }
8948 }
8949
8950 auto positionForDragEnd = WebCore::roundedIntPoint(_dragDropInteractionState.adjustedPositionForDragEnd());
8951 RetainPtr<WKContentView> protectedSelf(self);
8952 [animator addCompletion:[session, positionForDragEnd, protectedSelf, page = _page] (UIViewAnimatingPosition finalPosition) {
8953#if RELEASE_LOG_DISABLED
8954 UNUSED_PARAM(session);
8955#endif
8956 if (finalPosition == UIViewAnimatingPositionStart) {
8957 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session ended at start: %p", session);
8958 // The lift was canceled, so -dropInteraction:sessionDidEnd: will never be invoked. This is the last chance to clean up.
8959 [protectedSelf cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
8960 page->dragEnded(positionForDragEnd, positionForDragEnd, { });
8961 }
8962#if !RELEASE_LOG_DISABLED
8963 else
8964 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session did not end at start: %p", session);
8965#endif
8966 }];
8967}
8968
8969- (void)dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction sessionWillBegin:(id <UIDragSession>)session
8970{
8971 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session beginning: %p", session);
8972 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = self.webViewUIDelegate;
8973 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:dataInteraction:sessionWillBegin:)])
8974 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView dataInteraction:interaction sessionWillBegin:session];
8975
8976 [_actionSheetAssistant cleanupSheet];
8977 _dragDropInteractionState.dragSessionWillBegin();
8978 _page->didStartDrag();
8979}

8981- (void)dragInteraction:(UIDragInteraction *)interaction session:(id <UIDragSession>)session didEndWithOperation:(UIDropOperation)operation
8982{
8983 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drag session ended: %p (with operation: %tu, performing operation: %d, began dragging: %d)", session, operation, _dragDropInteractionState.isPerformingDrop(), _dragDropInteractionState.didBeginDragging());
8984
8985 [self _restoreCalloutBarIfNeeded];
8986
8987 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = self.webViewUIDelegate;
8988 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:dataInteraction:session:didEndWithOperation:)])
8989 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView dataInteraction:interaction session:session didEndWithOperation:operation];
8990
8991 if (_dragDropInteractionState.isPerformingDrop())
8992 return;
8993
8994 [self cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
8995 _page->dragEnded(WebCore::roundedIntPoint(_dragDropInteractionState.adjustedPositionForDragEnd()), WebCore::roundedIntPoint(_dragDropInteractionState.adjustedPositionForDragEnd()), coreDragOperationForUIDropOperation(operation));
8996}

9047- (BOOL)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction canHandleSession:(id<UIDropSession>)session
9048{
9049 // FIXME: Support multiple simultaneous drop sessions in the future.
9050 id <UIDragDropSession> dragOrDropSession = self.currentDragOrDropSession;
9051 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Can handle drag session: %p with local session: %p existing session: %p?", session, session.localDragSession, dragOrDropSession);
9052
9053 return !dragOrDropSession || session.localDragSession == dragOrDropSession;
9054}
9055
9056- (void)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction sessionDidEnter:(id <UIDropSession>)session
9057{
9058 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drop session entered: %p with %tu items", session, session.items.count);
9059 auto dragData = [self dragDataForDropSession:session dragDestinationAction:[self _dragDestinationActionForDropSession:session]];
9060
9061 _dragDropInteractionState.dropSessionDidEnterOrUpdate(session, dragData);
9062
9063 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] setItemProviders:extractItemProvidersFromDropSession(session)];
9064 _page->dragEntered(dragData, WebCore::Pasteboard::nameOfDragPasteboard());
9065}
9066
9067- (UIDropProposal *)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction sessionDidUpdate:(id <UIDropSession>)session
9068{
9069 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] setItemProviders:extractItemProvidersFromDropSession(session)];
9070
9071 auto dragData = [self dragDataForDropSession:session dragDestinationAction:[self _dragDestinationActionForDropSession:session]];
9072 _page->dragUpdated(dragData, WebCore::Pasteboard::nameOfDragPasteboard());
9073 _dragDropInteractionState.dropSessionDidEnterOrUpdate(session, dragData);
9074
9075 auto delegate = self.webViewUIDelegate;
9076 auto operation = dropOperationForWebCoreDragOperation(_page->currentDragOperation());
9077 if ([delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:willUpdateDataInteractionOperationToOperation:forSession:)])
9078 operation = static_cast<UIDropOperation>([delegate _webView:self.webView willUpdateDataInteractionOperationToOperation:operation forSession:session]);
9079
9080 auto proposal = adoptNS([[UIDropProposal alloc] initWithDropOperation:static_cast<UIDropOperation>(operation)]);
9081 auto dragHandlingMethod = _page->currentDragHandlingMethod();
9082 if (dragHandlingMethod == WebCore::DragHandlingMethod::EditPlainText || dragHandlingMethod == WebCore::DragHandlingMethod::EditRichText) {
9083 // When dragging near the top or bottom edges of an editable element, enabling precision drop mode may result in the drag session hit-testing outside of the editable
9084 // element, causing the drag to no longer be accepted. This in turn disables precision drop mode, which causes the drag session to hit-test inside of the editable
9085 // element again, which enables precision mode, thus continuing the cycle. To avoid precision mode thrashing, we forbid precision mode when dragging near the top or
9086 // bottom of the editable element.
9087 auto minimumDistanceFromVerticalEdgeForPreciseDrop = 25 / self.webView.scrollView.zoomScale;
9088 [proposal setPrecise:CGRectContainsPoint(CGRectInset(_page->currentDragCaretEditableElementRect(), 0, minimumDistanceFromVerticalEdgeForPreciseDrop), [session locationInView:self])];
9089 } else
9090 [proposal setPrecise:NO];
9091
9092 if ([delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:willUpdateDropProposalToProposal:forSession:)])
9093 proposal = [delegate _webView:self.webView willUpdateDropProposalToProposal:proposal.get() forSession:session];
9094
9095 return proposal.autorelease();
9096}
9097
9098- (void)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction sessionDidExit:(id <UIDropSession>)session
9099{
9100 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drop session exited: %p with %tu items", session, session.items.count);
9101 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] setItemProviders:extractItemProvidersFromDropSession(session)];
9102
9103 auto dragData = [self dragDataForDropSession:session dragDestinationAction:WKDragDestinationActionAny];
9104 _page->dragExited(dragData, WebCore::Pasteboard::nameOfDragPasteboard());
9105 _page->resetCurrentDragInformation();
9106
9107 _dragDropInteractionState.dropSessionDidExit();
9108}
9109
9110- (void)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction performDrop:(id <UIDropSession>)session
9111{
9112 NSArray <NSItemProvider *> *itemProviders = extractItemProvidersFromDropSession(session);
9113 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = self.webViewUIDelegate;
9114 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:performDataInteractionOperationWithItemProviders:)]) {
9115 if ([uiDelegate _webView:self.webView performDataInteractionOperationWithItemProviders:itemProviders])
9116 return;
9117 }
9118
9119 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:willPerformDropWithSession:)]) {
9120 itemProviders = extractItemProvidersFromDragItems([uiDelegate _webView:self.webView willPerformDropWithSession:session]);
9121 if (!itemProviders.count)
9122 return;
9123 }
9124
9125 _dragDropInteractionState.dropSessionWillPerformDrop();
9126
9127 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] setItemProviders:itemProviders];
9128 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] incrementPendingOperationCount];
9129 auto dragData = [self dragDataForDropSession:session dragDestinationAction:WKDragDestinationActionAny];
9130 BOOL shouldSnapshotView = ![self _handleDropByInsertingImagePlaceholders:itemProviders session:session];
9131
9132 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Loading data from %tu item providers for session: %p", itemProviders.count, session);
9133 // Always loading content from the item provider ensures that the web process will be allowed to call back in to the UI
9134 // process to access pasteboard contents at a later time. Ideally, we only need to do this work if we're over a file input
9135 // or the page prevented default on `dragover`, but without this, dropping into a normal editable areas will fail due to
9136 // item providers not loading any data.
9137 RetainPtr<WKContentView> retainedSelf(self);
9138 [[WebItemProviderPasteboard sharedInstance] doAfterLoadingProvidedContentIntoFileURLs:[retainedSelf, capturedDragData = WTFMove(dragData), shouldSnapshotView] (NSArray *fileURLs) mutable {
9139 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Loaded data into %tu files", fileURLs.count);
9140 Vector<String> filenames;
9141 for (NSURL *fileURL in fileURLs)
9142 filenames.append([fileURL path]);
9143 capturedDragData.setFileNames(filenames);
9144
9145 WebKit::SandboxExtension::Handle sandboxExtensionHandle;
9146 WebKit::SandboxExtension::HandleArray sandboxExtensionForUpload;
9147 auto dragPasteboardName = WebCore::Pasteboard::nameOfDragPasteboard();
9148 retainedSelf->_page->grantAccessToCurrentPasteboardData(dragPasteboardName);
9149 retainedSelf->_page->createSandboxExtensionsIfNeeded(filenames, sandboxExtensionHandle, sandboxExtensionForUpload);
9150 retainedSelf->_page->performDragOperation(capturedDragData, dragPasteboardName, WTFMove(sandboxExtensionHandle), WTFMove(sandboxExtensionForUpload));
9151 if (shouldSnapshotView) {
9152 retainedSelf->_visibleContentViewSnapshot = [retainedSelf snapshotViewAfterScreenUpdates:NO];
9153 [retainedSelf->_visibleContentViewSnapshot setFrame:[retainedSelf bounds]];
9154 [retainedSelf addSubview:retainedSelf->_visibleContentViewSnapshot.get()];
9155 }
9156 }];
9157}
9158
9159- (void)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction item:(UIDragItem *)item willAnimateDropWithAnimator:(id <UIDragAnimating>)animator
9160{
9161 _dropAnimationCount++;
9162 [animator addCompletion:[strongSelf = retainPtr(self)] (UIViewAnimatingPosition) {
9163 if (!--strongSelf->_dropAnimationCount)
9164 [std::exchange(strongSelf->_unselectedContentSnapshot, nil) removeFromSuperview];
9165 }];
9166}
9167
9168- (void)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction concludeDrop:(id <UIDropSession>)session
9169{
9170 [self _removeContainerForDropPreviews];
9171 [std::exchange(_visibleContentViewSnapshot, nil) removeFromSuperview];
9172 [std::exchange(_unselectedContentSnapshot, nil) removeFromSuperview];
9173 _dragDropInteractionState.clearAllDelayedItemPreviewProviders();
9174 _page->didConcludeDrop();
9175}
9176
9177- (UITargetedDragPreview *)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction previewForDroppingItem:(UIDragItem *)item withDefault:(UITargetedDragPreview *)defaultPreview
9178{
9179 _dragDropInteractionState.setDefaultDropPreview(item, defaultPreview);
9180
9181 CGRect caretRect = _page->currentDragCaretRect();
9182 if (CGRectIsEmpty(caretRect))
9183 return nil;
9184
9185 UIView *textEffectsWindow = self.textEffectsWindow;
9186 auto caretRectInWindowCoordinates = [self convertRect:caretRect toView:textEffectsWindow];
9187 auto caretCenterInWindowCoordinates = CGPointMake(CGRectGetMidX(caretRectInWindowCoordinates), CGRectGetMidY(caretRectInWindowCoordinates));
9188 auto targetPreviewCenterInWindowCoordinates = CGPointMake(caretCenterInWindowCoordinates.x + defaultPreview.size.width / 2, caretCenterInWindowCoordinates.y + defaultPreview.size.height / 2);
9189 auto target = adoptNS([[UIDragPreviewTarget alloc] initWithContainer:textEffectsWindow center:targetPreviewCenterInWindowCoordinates transform:CGAffineTransformIdentity]);
9190 return [defaultPreview retargetedPreviewWithTarget:target.get()];
9191}

9193- (void)_dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction delayedPreviewProviderForDroppingItem:(UIDragItem *)item previewProvider:(void(^)(UITargetedDragPreview *preview))previewProvider
9194{
9195 // FIXME: This doesn't currently handle multiple items in a drop session.
9196 _dragDropInteractionState.prepareForDelayedDropPreview(item, previewProvider);
9197}
9198
9199- (void)dropInteraction:(UIDropInteraction *)interaction sessionDidEnd:(id <UIDropSession>)session
9200{
9201 RELEASE_LOG(DragAndDrop, "Drop session ended: %p (performing operation: %d, began dragging: %d)", session, _dragDropInteractionState.isPerformingDrop(), _dragDropInteractionState.didBeginDragging());
9202 if (_dragDropInteractionState.isPerformingDrop()) {
9203 // In the case where we are performing a drop, wait until after the drop is handled in the web process to reset drag and drop interaction state.
9204 return;
9205 }
9206
9207 if (_dragDropInteractionState.didBeginDragging()) {
9208 // In the case where the content view is a source of drag items, wait until -dragInteraction:session:didEndWithOperation: to reset drag and drop interaction state.
9209 return;
9210 }
9211
9212 CGPoint global;
9213 CGPoint client;
9214 [self computeClientAndGlobalPointsForDropSession:session outClientPoint:&client outGlobalPoint:&global];
9215 [self cleanUpDragSourceSessionState];
9216 _page->dragEnded(WebCore::roundedIntPoint(client), WebCore::roundedIntPoint(global), { });
9217}

9221#if HAVE(PEPPER_UI_CORE)
9222
9223- (void)dismissQuickboardViewControllerAndRevealFocusedFormOverlayIfNecessary:(id)controller
9224{
9225 BOOL shouldRevealFocusOverlay = NO;
9226 // In the case where there's nothing the user could potentially do besides dismiss the overlay, we can just automatically without asking the delegate.
9227 if ([self.webView._inputDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:shouldRevealFocusOverlayForInputSession:)]
9228 && ([self actionNameForFocusedFormControlView:_focusedFormControlView.get()] || _focusedElementInformation.hasNextNode || _focusedElementInformation.hasPreviousNode))
9229 shouldRevealFocusOverlay = [self.webView._inputDelegate _webView:self.webView shouldRevealFocusOverlayForInputSession:_formInputSession.get()];
9230
9231 if (shouldRevealFocusOverlay) {
9232 [_focusedFormControlView show:NO];
9233 [self updateCurrentFocusedElementInformation:[weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self)] (bool didUpdate) {
9234 if (!didUpdate)
9235 return;
9236
9237 auto focusedFormController = weakSelf.get()->_focusedFormControlView;
9238 [focusedFormController reloadData:YES];
9239 [focusedFormController engageFocusedFormControlNavigation];
9240 }];
9241 } else
9242 _page->blurFocusedElement();
9243
9244 bool shouldDismissViewController = [controller isKindOfClass:UIViewController.class]
9245#if HAVE(QUICKBOARD_CONTROLLER)
9246 && !_presentedQuickboardController
9247#endif
9248 && controller != _presentedFullScreenInputViewController;
9249 // The Quickboard view controller passed into this delegate method is not necessarily the view controller we originally presented;
9250 // this happens in the case when the user chooses an input method (e.g. scribble) and a new Quickboard view controller is presented.
9251 if (shouldDismissViewController)
9252 [(UIViewController *)controller dismissViewControllerAnimated:YES completion:nil];
9253
9254 [self dismissAllInputViewControllers:controller == _presentedFullScreenInputViewController];
9255}

9257- (UITextContentType)textContentTypeForQuickboard
9258{
9259 switch (_focusedElementInformation.elementType) {
9260 case WebKit::InputType::Password:
9261 return UITextContentTypePassword;
9262 case WebKit::InputType::URL:
9263 return UITextContentTypeURL;
9264 case WebKit::InputType::Email:
9265 return UITextContentTypeEmailAddress;
9266 case WebKit::InputType::Phone:
9267 return UITextContentTypeTelephoneNumber;
9268 default:
9269 // The element type alone is insufficient to infer content type; fall back to autofill data.
9270 if (auto contentType = contentTypeFromFieldName(_focusedElementInformation.autofillFieldName))
9271 return contentType;
9272
9273 if (_focusedElementInformation.isAutofillableUsernameField)
9274 return UITextContentTypeUsername;
9275
9276 return nil;
9277 }
9278}

9419#if HAVE(UIKIT_WITH_MOUSE_SUPPORT)
9420
9421static BOOL applicationIsKnownToIgnoreMouseEvents(const char* &warningVersion)
9422{
9423 // System apps will always be linked on the current OS, so
9424 // check them before the linked-on-or-after.
9425
9426 // <rdar://problem/59521967> iAd Video does not respond to mouse events, only touch events
9427 if (WebCore::IOSApplication::isNews() || WebCore::IOSApplication::isStocks()) {
9428 warningVersion = nullptr;
9429 return YES;
9430 }
9431
9432 if (!WebCore::linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstVersionWithiOSAppsOnMacOS)) {
9433 if (WebCore::IOSApplication::isFIFACompanion() // <rdar://problem/67093487>
9434 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isNoggin() // <rdar://problem/64830335>
9435 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isOKCupid() // <rdar://problem/65698496>
9436 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isJWLibrary() // <rdar://problem/68104852>
9437 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isPaperIO() // <rdar://problem/68738585>
9438 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isCrunchyroll()) { // <rdar://problem/66362029>
9439 warningVersion = "14.2";
9440 return YES;
9441 }
9442 }
9443
9444 if (!WebCore::linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstThatSendsNativeMouseEvents)) {
9445 if (WebCore::IOSApplication::isPocketCity() // <rdar://problem/62273077>
9446 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isEssentialSkeleton() // <rdar://problem/62694519>
9447 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isESPNFantasySports() // <rdar://problem/64671543>
9448 || WebCore::IOSApplication::isDoubleDown()) { // <rdar://problem/64668138>
9449 warningVersion = "13.4";
9450 return YES;
9451 }
9452 }
9453
9454 return NO;
9455}
9456
9457- (BOOL)shouldUseMouseGestureRecognizer
9458{
9459 static const BOOL shouldUseMouseGestureRecognizer = []() -> BOOL {
9460 const char* warningVersion = nullptr;
9461 BOOL knownToIgnoreMouseEvents = applicationIsKnownToIgnoreMouseEvents(warningVersion);
9462
9463 if (knownToIgnoreMouseEvents && warningVersion)
9464 os_log_error(OS_LOG_DEFAULT, "WARNING: This application has been observed to ignore mouse events in web content; touch events will be sent until it is built against the iOS %s SDK, but after that, the web content must respect mouse or pointer events in addition to touch events in order to behave correctly when a trackpad or mouse is used.", warningVersion);
9465
9466 return !knownToIgnoreMouseEvents;
9467 }();
9468
9469 switch (_mouseEventPolicy) {
9470 case WebCore::MouseEventPolicy::Default:
9471 break;
9472#if ENABLE(IOS_TOUCH_EVENTS)
9473 case WebCore::MouseEventPolicy::SynthesizeTouchEvents:
9474 return NO;
9475#endif
9476 }
9477
9478 return shouldUseMouseGestureRecognizer;
9479}
9480
9481- (void)setUpMouseGestureRecognizer
9482{
9483 _mouseGestureRecognizer = adoptNS([[WKMouseGestureRecognizer alloc] initWithTarget:self action:@selector(mouseGestureRecognizerChanged:)]);
9484 [_mouseGestureRecognizer setDelegate:self];
9485 [self _configureMouseGestureRecognizer];
9486 [self addGestureRecognizer:_mouseGestureRecognizer.get()];
9487}
9488
9489- (void)mouseGestureRecognizerChanged:(WKMouseGestureRecognizer *)gestureRecognizer
9490{
9491 if (!_page->hasRunningProcess())
9492 return;
9493
9494 auto event = gestureRecognizer.lastMouseEvent;
9495 if (!event)
9496 return;
9497
9498 if (event->type() == WebKit::WebEvent::MouseDown)
9499 _layerTreeTransactionIdAtLastInteractionStart = downcast<WebKit::RemoteLayerTreeDrawingAreaProxy>(*_page->drawingArea()).lastCommittedLayerTreeTransactionID();
9500
9501 if (event->type() == WebKit::WebEvent::MouseUp && self.hasHiddenContentEditable && self._hasFocusedElement && !self.window.keyWindow)
9502 [self.window makeKeyWindow];
9503
9504 _page->handleMouseEvent(*event);
9505}
9506
9507- (void)_configureMouseGestureRecognizer
9508{
9509 [_mouseGestureRecognizer setEnabled:[self shouldUseMouseGestureRecognizer]];
9510}
9511
9512- (void)_setMouseEventPolicy:(WebCore::MouseEventPolicy)policy
9513{
9514 _mouseEventPolicy = policy;
9515 [self _configureMouseGestureRecognizer];
9516}

9554- (void)setUpPointerInteraction
9555{
9556 _pointerInteraction = adoptNS([[UIPointerInteraction alloc] initWithDelegate:self]);
9557 [_pointerInteraction _setPausesPointerUpdatesWhilePanning:NO];
