9561
9562- (void)_pointerInteraction:(UIPointerInteraction *)interaction regionForRequest:(UIPointerRegionRequest *)request defaultRegion:(UIPointerRegion *)defaultRegion completion:(void(^)(UIPointerRegion *region))completion
9563{
9564 WebKit::InteractionInformationRequest interactionInformationRequest;
9565 interactionInformationRequest.point = WebCore::roundedIntPoint(request.location);
9566 interactionInformationRequest.includeCaretContext = true;
9567 interactionInformationRequest.includeHasDoubleClickHandler = false;
9568
9569 BOOL didSynchronouslyReplyWithApproximation = false;
9570 if (![self _currentPositionInformationIsValidForRequest:interactionInformationRequest] && self.webView._editable && !_positionInformation.shouldNotUseIBeamInEditableContent) {
9571 didSynchronouslyReplyWithApproximation = true;
9572 completion([UIPointerRegion regionWithRect:self.bounds identifier:editablePointerRegionIdentifier]);
9573 }
9574
9575 // If we already have an outstanding interaction information request, defer this one until
9576 // we hear back, so that requests don't pile up if the Web Content process is slow.
9577 if (_hasOutstandingPointerInteractionRequest) {
9578 _deferredPointerInteractionRequest = std::make_pair(interactionInformationRequest, makeBlockPtr(completion));
9579 return;
9580 }
9581
9582 _hasOutstandingPointerInteractionRequest = YES;
9583
9584 __block BlockPtr<void(WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition, void(^)(UIPointerRegion *))> replyHandler;
9585 replyHandler = ^(WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition interactionInformation, void(^completion)(UIPointerRegion *region)) {
9586 if (!_deferredPointerInteractionRequest)
9587 _hasOutstandingPointerInteractionRequest = NO;
9588
9589 if (didSynchronouslyReplyWithApproximation) {
9590 [interaction invalidate];
9591 return;
9592 }
9593
9594 completion([self pointerRegionForPositionInformation:interactionInformation point:request.location]);
9595
9596 if (_deferredPointerInteractionRequest) {
9597 auto deferredRequest = std::exchange(_deferredPointerInteractionRequest, std::nullopt);
9598 [self doAfterPositionInformationUpdate:^(WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition interactionInformation) {
9599 replyHandler(interactionInformation, deferredRequest->second.get());
9600 } forRequest:deferredRequest->first];
9601 return;
9602 }
9603 };
9604
9605 [self doAfterPositionInformationUpdate:^(WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition interactionInformation) {
9606 replyHandler(interactionInformation, completion);
9607 } forRequest:interactionInformationRequest];
9608}
9609
9610- (UIPointerRegion *)pointerRegionForPositionInformation:(WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition&)interactionInformation point:(CGPoint)location
9611{
9612 WebCore::FloatRect expandedLineRect = enclosingIntRect(interactionInformation.lineCaretExtent);
9613
9614 // Pad lines of text in order to avoid switching back to the dot cursor between lines.
9615 // This matches the value that UIKit uses.
9616 expandedLineRect.inflateY(10);
9617
9618 if (interactionInformation.cursor) {
9619 WebCore::Cursor::Type cursorType = interactionInformation.cursor->type();
9620 if (cursorType == WebCore::Cursor::Hand)
9621 return [UIPointerRegion regionWithRect:interactionInformation.bounds identifier:pointerRegionIdentifier];
9622
9623 if (cursorType == WebCore::Cursor::IBeam && expandedLineRect.contains(location))
9624 return [UIPointerRegion regionWithRect:expandedLineRect identifier:pointerRegionIdentifier];
9625 }
9626
9627 if (self.webView._editable) {
9628 if (expandedLineRect.contains(location))
9629 return [UIPointerRegion regionWithRect:expandedLineRect identifier:pointerRegionIdentifier];
9630 return [UIPointerRegion regionWithRect:self.bounds identifier:editablePointerRegionIdentifier];
9631 }
9632
9633 return nil;
9634}
9635
9636- (UIPointerStyle *)pointerInteraction:(UIPointerInteraction *)interaction styleForRegion:(UIPointerRegion *)region
9637{
9638 double scaleFactor = self._contentZoomScale;
9639
9640 UIPointerStyle *(^iBeamCursor)(void) = ^{
9641 float beamLength = _positionInformation.caretLength * scaleFactor;
9642 auto axisOrientation = _positionInformation.isHorizontalWritingMode ? UIAxisVertical : UIAxisHorizontal;
9643 UIAxis iBeamConstraintAxes = _positionInformation.isHorizontalWritingMode ? UIAxisVertical : UIAxisHorizontal;
9644
9645 // If the I-beam is so large that the magnetism is hard to fight, we should not apply any magnetism.
9646 if (beamLength > [UITextInteraction _maximumBeamSnappingLength])
9647 iBeamConstraintAxes = UIAxisNeither;
9648
9649 // If the region is the size of the view, we should not apply any magnetism.
9650 if ([region.identifier isEqual:editablePointerRegionIdentifier])
9651 iBeamConstraintAxes = UIAxisNeither;
9652
9653 return [UIPointerStyle styleWithShape:[UIPointerShape beamWithPreferredLength:beamLength axis:axisOrientation] constrainedAxes:iBeamConstraintAxes];
9654 };
9655
9656 if (self.webView._editable) {
9657 if (_positionInformation.shouldNotUseIBeamInEditableContent)
9658 return nil;
9659 return iBeamCursor();
9660 }
9661
9662 if (_positionInformation.cursor && [region.identifier isEqual:pointerRegionIdentifier]) {
9663 WebCore::Cursor::Type cursorType = _positionInformation.cursor->type();
9664
9665 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
9666 if (cursorType == WebCore::Cursor::Hand)
9667 return [UIPointerStyle _systemPointerStyle];
9668 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
9669
9670 if (cursorType == WebCore::Cursor::IBeam && _positionInformation.lineCaretExtent.contains(_positionInformation.request.point))
9671 return iBeamCursor();
9672 }
9673
9674 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
9675 return nil;
9676}

9678#endif // HAVE(UI_POINTER_INTERACTION)

9757#if !PLATFORM(WATCHOS) && !PLATFORM(APPLETV)
9758
9759static RetainPtr<NSItemProvider> createItemProvider(const WebKit::WebPageProxy& page, const WebCore::PromisedAttachmentInfo& info)
9760{
9761 auto numberOfAdditionalTypes = info.additionalTypes.size();
9762 ASSERT(numberOfAdditionalTypes == info.additionalData.size());
9763
9764 auto attachment = page.attachmentForIdentifier(info.attachmentIdentifier);
9765 if (!attachment)
9766 return { };
9767
9768 NSString *utiType = attachment->utiType();
9769 if (![utiType length])
9770 return { };
9771
9772 auto fileWrapper = retainPtr(attachment->fileWrapper());
9773 if (!fileWrapper)
9774 return { };
9775
9776 auto item = adoptNS([[NSItemProvider alloc] init]);
9777 [item setPreferredPresentationStyle:UIPreferredPresentationStyleAttachment];
9778
9779 NSString *fileName = attachment->fileName();
9780 if ([fileName length])
9781 [item setSuggestedName:fileName];
9782
9783 if (numberOfAdditionalTypes == info.additionalData.size() && numberOfAdditionalTypes) {
9784 for (size_t index = 0; index < numberOfAdditionalTypes; ++index) {
9785 auto nsData = info.additionalData[index]->createNSData();
9786 [item registerDataRepresentationForTypeIdentifier:info.additionalTypes[index] visibility:NSItemProviderRepresentationVisibilityAll loadHandler:[nsData](void (^completionHandler)(NSData *, NSError *)) -> NSProgress * {
9787 completionHandler(nsData.get(), nil);
9788 return nil;
9789 }];
9790 }
9791 }
9792
9793 [item registerDataRepresentationForTypeIdentifier:utiType visibility:NSItemProviderRepresentationVisibilityAll loadHandler:[fileWrapper](void (^completionHandler)(NSData *, NSError *)) -> NSProgress * {
9794 if (auto nsData = retainPtr([fileWrapper serializedRepresentation]))
9795 completionHandler(nsData.get(), nil);
9796 else
9797 completionHandler(nil, [NSError errorWithDomain:WKErrorDomain code:WKErrorUnknown userInfo:nil]);
9798 return nil;
9799 }];
9800
9801 return item;
9802}
9803
9804#endif // !PLATFORM(WATCHOS) && !PLATFORM(APPLETV)
9805
9806- (void)_writePromisedAttachmentToPasteboard:(WebCore::PromisedAttachmentInfo&&)info
9807{
9808#if !PLATFORM(WATCHOS) && !PLATFORM(APPLETV)
9809 if (auto item = createItemProvider(*_page, WTFMove(info)))
9810 UIPasteboard.generalPasteboard.itemProviders = @[ item.get() ];
9811#else
9812 UNUSED_PARAM(info);
9813#endif
9814}
9815
9816#endif // ENABLE(ATTACHMENT_ELEMENT)

9825- (void)_doAfterPendingImageAnalysis:(void(^)(WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage))block
9826{
9827 if (self.hasPendingImageAnalysisRequest)
9828 _actionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis.append(makeBlockPtr(block));
9829 else
9830 block(WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No);
9831}
9832
9833- (void)_invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:(WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage)ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage
9834{
9835 _pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier = std::nullopt;
9836 _elementPendingImageAnalysis = std::nullopt;
9837 for (auto block : std::exchange(_actionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis, { }))
9838 block(ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage);
9839}

9843- (void)setUpTextIndicator:(Ref<WebCore::TextIndicator>)textIndicator
9844{
9845 if (_textIndicator == textIndicator.ptr())
9846 return;
9847
9848 [self teardownTextIndicatorLayer];
9849 [NSObject cancelPreviousPerformRequestsWithTarget:self selector:@selector(startFadeOut) object:nil];
9850
9851 _textIndicator = textIndicator.ptr();
9852
9853 CGRect frame = _textIndicator->textBoundingRectInRootViewCoordinates();
9854 _textIndicatorLayer = adoptNS([[WebTextIndicatorLayer alloc] initWithFrame:frame
9855 textIndicator:textIndicator margin:CGSizeZero offset:CGPointZero]);
9856
9857 [[self layer] addSublayer:_textIndicatorLayer.get()];
9858
9859 if (_textIndicator->presentationTransition() != WebCore::TextIndicatorPresentationTransition::None)
9860 [_textIndicatorLayer present];
9861
9862 [self performSelector:@selector(startFadeOut) withObject:self afterDelay:WebCore::timeBeforeFadeStarts.value()];
9863}
9864
9865- (void)clearTextIndicator:(WebCore::TextIndicatorDismissalAnimation)animation
9866{
9867 RefPtr<WebCore::TextIndicator> textIndicator = WTFMove(_textIndicator);
9868
9869 if ([_textIndicatorLayer isFadingOut])
9870 return;
9871
9872 if (textIndicator && [_textIndicatorLayer indicatorWantsManualAnimation:*textIndicator] && [_textIndicatorLayer hasCompletedAnimation] && animation == WebCore::TextIndicatorDismissalAnimation::FadeOut) {
9873 [self startFadeOut];
9874 return;
9875 }
9876
9877 [self teardownTextIndicatorLayer];
9878}
9879
9880- (void)setTextIndicatorAnimationProgress:(float)animationProgress
9881{
9882 if (!_textIndicator)
9883 return;
9884
9885 [_textIndicatorLayer setAnimationProgress:animationProgress];
9886}

9897
9898 [_textIndicatorLayer hideWithCompletionHandler:[weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self)] {
9899 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
9900 [strongSelf teardownTextIndicatorLayer];
9901 }];
9902}

9986 ASSERT(_visualSearchPreviewImage);

10035- (void)_setUpImageAnalysis
10036{
10037 if (!WebKit::isLiveTextAvailableAndEnabled())
10038 return;
10039
10040 _pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier = std::nullopt;
10041 _isProceedingWithTextSelectionInImage = NO;
10042 _elementPendingImageAnalysis = std::nullopt;
10043 _imageAnalysisGestureRecognizer = adoptNS([[WKImageAnalysisGestureRecognizer alloc] initWithImageAnalysisGestureDelegate:self]);
10044 [self addGestureRecognizer:_imageAnalysisGestureRecognizer.get()];
10045 _imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer = adoptNS([[UILongPressGestureRecognizer alloc] initWithTarget:self action:@selector(imageAnalysisGestureDidTimeOut:)]);
10046 [_imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer setMinimumPressDuration:2.0];
10047 [_imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer setName:@"Image analysis timeout"];
10048 [_imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer setDelegate:self];
10049 [self addGestureRecognizer:_imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer.get()];
10050#if USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10051 _hasSelectableTextInImage = NO;
10052 _hasVisualSearchResults = NO;
10053#endif // USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10054#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10055 _contextMenuForMachineReadableCode.clear();
10056#endif // USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10057}

10059- (void)_tearDownImageAnalysis
10060{
10061 if (!WebKit::isLiveTextAvailableAndEnabled())
10062 return;
10063
10064 [_imageAnalysisGestureRecognizer setDelegate:nil];
10065 [self removeGestureRecognizer:_imageAnalysisGestureRecognizer.get()];
10066 _imageAnalysisGestureRecognizer = nil;
10067 [_imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer setDelegate:nil];
10068 [self removeGestureRecognizer:_imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer.get()];
10069 _imageAnalysisTimeoutGestureRecognizer = nil;
10070 _pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier = std::nullopt;
10071 _isProceedingWithTextSelectionInImage = NO;
10072 _elementPendingImageAnalysis = std::nullopt;
10073 [std::exchange(_imageAnalyzer, nil) cancelAllRequests];
10074#if USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10075 _hasSelectableTextInImage = NO;
10076 _hasVisualSearchResults = NO;
10077#endif // USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10078#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10079 _contextMenuForMachineReadableCode.clear();
10080#endif // USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10081 [self _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10082}

10087 RELEASE_LOG_IF(self.hasPendingImageAnalysisRequest, Images, "Image analysis request %" PRIu64 " cancelled.", _pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier->toUInt64());
10088 _pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier = std::nullopt;
10089 _isProceedingWithTextSelectionInImage = NO;
10090 _elementPendingImageAnalysis = std::nullopt;
10091}

10101- (RetainPtr<VKImageAnalyzerRequest>)createImageAnalysisRequest:(VKAnalysisTypes)analysisTypes image:(UIImage *)image

10106- (BOOL)validateImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier:(WebKit::ImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier)identifier
10107{
10108 if (_pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier == identifier)
10109 return YES;
10110
10111 if (!self.hasPendingImageAnalysisRequest) {
10112 // Only invoke deferred image analysis blocks if there is no ongoing request; otherwise, this would
10113 // cause these blocks to be invoked too early (i.e. in the middle of the new image analysis request).
10114 [self _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10115 }
10116
10117 RELEASE_LOG(Images, "Image analysis request %" PRIu64 " invalidated.", identifier.toUInt64());
10118 return NO;
10119}
10120
10121- (void)requestTextRecognition:(NSURL *)imageURL imageData:(const WebKit::ShareableBitmap::Handle&)imageData completionHandler:(CompletionHandler<void(WebCore::TextRecognitionResult&&)>&&)completion
10122{
10123 auto imageBitmap = WebKit::ShareableBitmap::create(imageData);
10124 if (!imageBitmap) {
10125 completion({ });
10126 return;
10127 }
10128
10129 auto cgImage = imageBitmap->makeCGImage();
10130 if (!cgImage) {
10131 completion({ });
10132 return;
10133 }
10134
10135 auto image = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage.get()]);
10136 if (!image) {
10137 completion({ });
10138 return;
10139 }
10140
10141 auto request = [self createImageAnalysisRequest:VKAnalysisTypeText image:image.get()];
10142 [[self imageAnalyzer] processRequest:request.get() progressHandler:nil completionHandler:makeBlockPtr([completion = WTFMove(completion)] (VKImageAnalysis *result, NSError *) mutable {
10143 completion(WebKit::makeTextRecognitionResult(result));
10144 }).get()];
10145}
10146
10147#pragma mark - WKImageAnalysisGestureRecognizerDelegate
10148
10149- (void)imageAnalysisGestureDidBegin:(WKImageAnalysisGestureRecognizer *)gestureRecognizer
10150{
10151 ASSERT(WebKit::isLiveTextAvailableAndEnabled());
10152
10153 auto requestIdentifier = WebKit::ImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier::generate();
10154
10155 [_imageAnalyzer cancelAllRequests];
10156 _pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier = requestIdentifier;
10157 _isProceedingWithTextSelectionInImage = NO;
10158 _elementPendingImageAnalysis = std::nullopt;
10159
10160#if USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10161 _hasSelectableTextInImage = NO;
10162 _hasVisualSearchResults = NO;
10163#endif // USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10164
10165#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10166 _contextMenuForMachineReadableCode.clear();
10167#endif // USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10168
10169 WebKit::InteractionInformationRequest request { WebCore::roundedIntPoint([gestureRecognizer locationInView:self]) };
10170 request.includeImageData = true;
10171 [self doAfterPositionInformationUpdate:[requestIdentifier = WTFMove(requestIdentifier), weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self), gestureDeferralToken = WebKit::ImageAnalysisGestureDeferralToken::create(self)] (WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition information) mutable {
10172 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10173 if (![strongSelf validateImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier:requestIdentifier])
10174 return;
10175
10176 bool shouldAnalyzeImageAtLocation = ([&] {
10177 if (!information.isImage)
10178 return false;
10179
10180 if (!information.image)
10181 return false;
10182
10183 if (!information.imageElementContext)
10184 return false;
10185
10186 if (information.isAnimatedImage)
10187 return false;
10188
10189 if (information.isContentEditable)
10190 return false;
10191
10192 return true;
10193 })();
10194
10195 if (!strongSelf->_pendingImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier || !shouldAnalyzeImageAtLocation) {
10196 [strongSelf _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10197 return;
10198 }
10199
10200 auto cgImage = information.image->makeCGImageCopy();
10201 if (!cgImage) {
10202 [strongSelf _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10203 return;
10204 }
10205
10206 auto image = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage.get()]);
10207 if (!image) {
10208 [strongSelf _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10209 return;
10210 }
10211
10212 RELEASE_LOG(Images, "Image analysis preflight gesture initiated (request %" PRIu64 ").", requestIdentifier.toUInt64());
10213
10214 strongSelf->_elementPendingImageAnalysis = information.imageElementContext;
10215
10216 auto requestLocation = information.request.point;
10217 WebCore::ElementContext elementContext = *information.imageElementContext;
10218
10219 auto requestForTextSelection = [strongSelf createImageAnalysisRequest:VKAnalysisTypeText image:image.get()];
10220 auto requestForContextMenu = [strongSelf createImageAnalysisRequest:VKAnalysisTypeVisualSearch | VKAnalysisTypeMachineReadableCode image:image.get()];
10221
10222 auto textAnalysisStartTime = MonotonicTime::now();
10223 [[strongSelf imageAnalyzer] processRequest:requestForTextSelection.get() progressHandler:nil completionHandler:[requestIdentifier = WTFMove(requestIdentifier), weakSelf, elementContext, requestLocation, requestForContextMenu, gestureDeferralToken, textAnalysisStartTime] (VKImageAnalysis *result, NSError *error) mutable {
10224 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10225 if (![strongSelf validateImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier:requestIdentifier])
10226 return;
10227
10228 BOOL hasTextResults = [result hasResultsForAnalysisTypes:VKAnalysisTypeText];
10229 RELEASE_LOG(Images, "Image analysis completed in %.0f ms (request %" PRIu64 "; found text? %d)", (MonotonicTime::now() - textAnalysisStartTime).milliseconds(), requestIdentifier.toUInt64(), hasTextResults);
10230
10231 strongSelf->_page->updateWithTextRecognitionResult(WebKit::makeTextRecognitionResult(result), elementContext, requestLocation, [requestIdentifier = WTFMove(requestIdentifier), weakSelf, hasTextResults, requestForContextMenu, gestureDeferralToken] (WebKit::TextRecognitionUpdateResult updateResult) mutable {
10232 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10233 if (![strongSelf validateImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier:requestIdentifier])
10234 return;
10235
10236 if (updateResult == WebKit::TextRecognitionUpdateResult::Text) {
10237 strongSelf->_isProceedingWithTextSelectionInImage = YES;
10238 [strongSelf _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::Yes];
10239 return;
10240 }
10241
10242 gestureDeferralToken->setShouldPreventTextSelection();
10243
10244 if (updateResult == WebKit::TextRecognitionUpdateResult::DataDetector) {
10245 [strongSelf _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10246 return;
10247 }
10248
10249 auto visualSearchAnalysisStartTime = MonotonicTime::now();
10250 [[strongSelf imageAnalyzer] processRequest:requestForContextMenu.get() progressHandler:nil completionHandler:[requestIdentifier = WTFMove(requestIdentifier), weakSelf, hasTextResults, visualSearchAnalysisStartTime] (VKImageAnalysis *result, NSError *error) mutable {
10251 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10252 if (![strongSelf validateImageAnalysisRequestIdentifier:requestIdentifier])
10253 return;
10254
10255#if USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10256 BOOL hasVisualSearchResults = [result hasResultsForAnalysisTypes:VKAnalysisTypeVisualSearch];
10257 RELEASE_LOG(Images, "Image analysis completed in %.0f ms (request %" PRIu64 "; found visual search results? %d)", (MonotonicTime::now() - visualSearchAnalysisStartTime).milliseconds(), requestIdentifier.toUInt64(), hasVisualSearchResults);
10258#else
10259 UNUSED_PARAM(visualSearchAnalysisStartTime);
10260#endif
10261 if (!result || error) {
10262 [strongSelf _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10263 return;
10264 }
10265
10266#if USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10267 strongSelf->_hasSelectableTextInImage = hasTextResults;
10268 strongSelf->_hasVisualSearchResults = hasVisualSearchResults;
10269#else
10270 UNUSED_PARAM(hasTextResults);
10271#endif
10272#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10273 strongSelf->_contextMenuForMachineReadableCode = [result hasResultsForAnalysisTypes:VKAnalysisTypeMachineReadableCode] ? result.mrcMenu : nil;
10274#endif
10275 [strongSelf _invokeAllActionsToPerformAfterPendingImageAnalysis:WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No];
10276 }];
10277 });
10278 }];
10279 } forRequest:request];
10280}
10281
10282- (void)imageAnalysisGestureDidFail:(WKImageAnalysisGestureRecognizer *)gestureRecognizer
10283{
10284 [self _endImageAnalysisGestureDeferral:WebKit::ShouldPreventGestures::No];
10285}
10286
10287- (void)imageAnalysisGestureDidTimeOut:(WKImageAnalysisGestureRecognizer *)gestureRecognizer
10288{
10289 if (!self._shouldUseContextMenus)
10290 return;
10291
10292 if (self.hasPendingImageAnalysisRequest)
10293 return;
10294
10295 if (gestureRecognizer.state != UIGestureRecognizerStateBegan)
10296 return;
10297
10298 auto location = WebCore::roundedIntPoint([gestureRecognizer locationInView:self]);
10299 WebKit::InteractionInformationRequest request { location };
10300 request.includeImageData = true;
10301 [self doAfterPositionInformationUpdate:[weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self), location] (WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition info) {
10302 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10303 if (!strongSelf)
10304 return;
10305
10306 if (!info.image)
10307 return;
10308
10309 if ((!info.isImageOverlayText || !info.isSelected) && !strongSelf->_isProceedingWithTextSelectionInImage)
10310 return;
10311
10312 auto cgImage = info.image->makeCGImageCopy();
10313 if (!cgImage)
10314 return;
10315
10316 auto image = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage.get()]);
10317 if (!image)
10318 return;
10319
10320 RELEASE_LOG(Images, "Image analysis timeout gesture initiated.");
10321 // FIXME: We need to implement some way to cache image analysis results per element, so that we don't end up
10322 // making redundant image analysis requests for the same image data.
10323
10324 auto visualSearchAnalysisStartTime = MonotonicTime::now();
10325 auto requestForContextMenu = [strongSelf createImageAnalysisRequest:VKAnalysisTypeVisualSearch | VKAnalysisTypeMachineReadableCode image:image.get()];
10326 [[strongSelf imageAnalyzer] processRequest:requestForContextMenu.get() progressHandler:nil completionHandler:[weakSelf, location, visualSearchAnalysisStartTime] (VKImageAnalysis *result, NSError *error) {
10327 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10328 if (!strongSelf)
10329 return;
10330
10331#if USE(QUICK_LOOK)
10332 BOOL hasVisualSearchResults = [result hasResultsForAnalysisTypes:VKAnalysisTypeVisualSearch];
10333 RELEASE_LOG(Images, "Image analysis completed in %.0f ms (found visual search results? %d)", (MonotonicTime::now() - visualSearchAnalysisStartTime).milliseconds(), hasVisualSearchResults);
10334 strongSelf->_hasSelectableTextInImage = YES;
10335 strongSelf->_hasVisualSearchResults = hasVisualSearchResults;
10336#else
10337 UNUSED_PARAM(visualSearchAnalysisStartTime);
10338#endif
10339
10340#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10341 strongSelf->_contextMenuForMachineReadableCode = [result hasResultsForAnalysisTypes:VKAnalysisTypeMachineReadableCode] ? result.mrcMenu : nil;
10342 strongSelf->_contextMenuWasTriggeredByImageAnalysisTimeout = YES;
10343 [strongSelf->_contextMenuInteraction _presentMenuAtLocation:location];
10344#else
10345 UNUSED_PARAM(location);
10346#endif
10347 }];
10348 } forRequest:request];
10349}

10600static NSString *previewIdentifierForElementAction(_WKElementAction *action)

10624- (void)_registerPreview
10625{
10626 if (!self.webView.allowsLinkPreview)
10627 return;
10628
10629#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10630 if (self._shouldUseContextMenus) {
10631 _contextMenuInteraction = adoptNS([[UIContextMenuInteraction alloc] initWithDelegate:self]);
10632 _contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData = NO;
10633 [self addInteraction:_contextMenuInteraction.get()];
10634
10635 if (id<_UIClickInteractionDriving> driver = self.webView.configuration._clickInteractionDriverForTesting) {
10636 _UIClickInteraction *previewClickInteraction = [[_contextMenuInteraction presentationInteraction] previewClickInteraction];
10637 [previewClickInteraction setDriver:driver];
10638 [driver setDelegate:(id<_UIClickInteractionDriverDelegate>)previewClickInteraction];
10639 }
10640 return;
10641 }
10642#endif
10643
10644 _previewItemController = adoptNS([[UIPreviewItemController alloc] initWithView:self]);
10645 [_previewItemController setDelegate:self];
10646 _previewGestureRecognizer = _previewItemController.get().presentationGestureRecognizer;
10647 if ([_previewItemController respondsToSelector:@selector(presentationSecondaryGestureRecognizer)])
10648 _previewSecondaryGestureRecognizer = _previewItemController.get().presentationSecondaryGestureRecognizer;
10649}
10650
10651- (void)_unregisterPreview
10652{
10653#if USE(UICONTEXTMENU)
10654 if (self._shouldUseContextMenus) {
10655 if (!_contextMenuInteraction)
10656 return;
10657
10658 [self removeInteraction:_contextMenuInteraction.get()];
10659 _contextMenuInteraction = nil;
10660 return;
10661 }
10662#endif
10663
10664 [_previewItemController setDelegate:nil];
10665 _previewGestureRecognizer = nil;
10666 _previewSecondaryGestureRecognizer = nil;
10667 _previewItemController = nil;
10668}

10671
10672static bool needsDeprecatedPreviewAPI(id<WKUIDelegate> delegate)
10673{
10674 // FIXME: Replace these with booleans in UIDelegate.h.
10675 // Note that we explicitly do not test for @selector(_webView:contextMenuDidEndForElement:)
10676 // and @selector(webView:contextMenuWillPresentForElement) since the methods are used by MobileSafari
10677 // to manage state despite the app not moving to the new API.
10678
10679 return delegate
10680 && ![delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:contextMenuConfigurationForElement:completionHandler:)]
10681 && ![delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:contextMenuConfigurationForElement:completionHandler:)]
10682 && ![delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:contextMenuForElement:willCommitWithAnimator:)]
10683 && ![delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:contextMenuForElement:willCommitWithAnimator:)]
10684 && ![delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:contextMenuWillPresentForElement:)]
10685 && ![delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:contextMenuDidEndForElement:)]
10686 && ([delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:shouldPreviewElement:)]
10687 || [delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:previewingViewControllerForElement:defaultActions:)]
10688 || [delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:commitPreviewingViewController:)]
10689 || [delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForURL:defaultActions:elementInfo:)]
10690 || [delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForURL:)]
10691 || [delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForImage:alternateURL:defaultActions:elementInfo:)]);
10692}
10693
10694ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
10695static NSArray<WKPreviewAction *> *wkLegacyPreviewActionsFromElementActions(NSArray<_WKElementAction *> *elementActions, _WKActivatedElementInfo *elementInfo)
10696{
10697 NSMutableArray<WKPreviewAction *> *previewActions = [NSMutableArray arrayWithCapacity:[elementActions count]];
10698 for (_WKElementAction *elementAction in elementActions) {
10699 WKPreviewAction *previewAction = [WKPreviewAction actionWithIdentifier:previewIdentifierForElementAction(elementAction) title:elementAction.title style:UIPreviewActionStyleDefault handler:^(UIPreviewAction *, UIViewController *) {
10700 [elementAction runActionWithElementInfo:elementInfo];
10701 }];
10702 previewAction.image = [_WKElementAction imageForElementActionType:elementAction.type];
10703 [previewActions addObject:previewAction];
10704 }
10705 return previewActions;
10706}
10707
10708static UIAction *uiActionForLegacyPreviewAction(UIPreviewAction *previewAction, UIViewController *previewViewController)
10709{
10710 // UIPreviewActionItem.image is SPI, so no external clients will be able
10711 // to provide glyphs for actions <rdar://problem/50151855>.
10712 // However, they should migrate to the new API.
10713
10714 return [UIAction actionWithTitle:previewAction.title image:previewAction.image identifier:nil handler:^(UIAction *action) {
10715 previewAction.handler(previewAction, previewViewController);
10716 }];
10717}
10718ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
10719
10720static NSArray<UIMenuElement *> *menuElementsFromLegacyPreview(UIViewController *previewViewController)
10721{
10722 if (!previewViewController)
10723 return nil;
10724
10725 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
10726 NSArray<id<UIPreviewActionItem>> *previewActions = previewViewController.previewActionItems;
10727 if (!previewActions || ![previewActions count])
10728 return nil;
10729
10730 auto actions = [NSMutableArray arrayWithCapacity:previewActions.count];
10731
10732 for (UIPreviewAction *previewAction in previewActions)
10733 [actions addObject:uiActionForLegacyPreviewAction(previewAction, previewViewController)];
10734 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
10735
10736 return actions;
10737}
10738
10739static NSMutableArray<UIMenuElement *> *menuElementsFromDefaultActions(const RetainPtr<NSArray>& defaultElementActions, RetainPtr<_WKActivatedElementInfo> elementInfo)
10740{
10741 if (!defaultElementActions || !defaultElementActions.get().count)
10742 return nil;
10743
10744 auto actions = [NSMutableArray arrayWithCapacity:defaultElementActions.get().count];
10745
10746 for (_WKElementAction *elementAction in defaultElementActions.get())
10747 [actions addObject:[elementAction uiActionForElementInfo:elementInfo.get()]];
10748
10749 return actions;
10750}
10751
10752static UIMenu *menuFromLegacyPreviewOrDefaultActions(UIViewController *previewViewController, const RetainPtr<NSArray>& defaultElementActions, RetainPtr<_WKActivatedElementInfo> elementInfo, NSString *title = nil)
10753{
10754 auto actions = menuElementsFromLegacyPreview(previewViewController);
10755 if (!actions)
10756 actions = menuElementsFromDefaultActions(defaultElementActions, elementInfo);
10757
10758 return [UIMenu menuWithTitle:title children:actions];
10759}
10760
10761- (void)assignLegacyDataForContextMenuInteraction
10762{
10763 ASSERT(!_contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData);
10764 if (_contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData)
10765 return;
10766 _contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData = YES;
10767
10768 if (!_webView)
10769 return;
10770 auto uiDelegate = static_cast<id<WKUIDelegatePrivate>>(self.webView.UIDelegate);
10771 if (!uiDelegate)
10772 return;
10773
10774 const auto& url = _positionInformation.url;
10775
10776 _page->startInteractionWithPositionInformation(_positionInformation);
10777
10778 RetainPtr<UIViewController> previewViewController;
10779
10780 auto elementInfo = adoptNS([[_WKActivatedElementInfo alloc] _initWithInteractionInformationAtPosition:_positionInformation userInfo:nil]);
10781
10782 ASSERT_IMPLIES(_positionInformation.isImage, _positionInformation.image);
10783 if (_positionInformation.isLink) {
10784 _longPressCanClick = NO;
10785
10786 RetainPtr<NSArray<_WKElementAction *>> defaultActionsFromAssistant = [_actionSheetAssistant defaultActionsForLinkSheet:elementInfo.get()];
10787
10788 // FIXME: Animated images go here.
10789
10790 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
10791 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:previewingViewControllerForElement:defaultActions:)]) {
10792 auto defaultActions = wkLegacyPreviewActionsFromElementActions(defaultActionsFromAssistant.get(), elementInfo.get());
10793 auto previewElementInfo = adoptNS([[WKPreviewElementInfo alloc] _initWithLinkURL:url]);
10794 // FIXME: Clients using this legacy API will always show their previewViewController and ignore _showLinkPreviews.
10795 previewViewController = [uiDelegate webView:self.webView previewingViewControllerForElement:previewElementInfo.get() defaultActions:defaultActions];
10796 } else if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForURL:defaultActions:elementInfo:)])
10797 previewViewController = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewViewControllerForURL:url defaultActions:defaultActionsFromAssistant.get() elementInfo:elementInfo.get()];
10798 else if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForURL:)])
10799 previewViewController = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewViewControllerForURL:url];
10800 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
10801
10802 // Previously, UIPreviewItemController would detect the case where there was no previewViewController
10803 // and create one. We need to replicate this code for the new API.
10804 if (!previewViewController || [(NSURL *)url iTunesStoreURL]) {
10805 auto ddContextMenuActionClass = getDDContextMenuActionClass();
10806 BEGIN_BLOCK_OBJC_EXCEPTIONS
10807 NSDictionary *context = [self dataDetectionContextForPositionInformation:_positionInformation];
10808 RetainPtr<UIContextMenuConfiguration> dataDetectorsResult = [ddContextMenuActionClass contextMenuConfigurationForURL:url identifier:_positionInformation.dataDetectorIdentifier selectedText:self.selectedText results:_positionInformation.dataDetectorResults.get() inView:self context:context menuIdentifier:nil];
10809 if (_showLinkPreviews && dataDetectorsResult && dataDetectorsResult.get().previewProvider)
10810 _contextMenuLegacyPreviewController = dataDetectorsResult.get().previewProvider();
10811 if (dataDetectorsResult && dataDetectorsResult.get().actionProvider) {
10812 auto menuElements = menuElementsFromDefaultActions(defaultActionsFromAssistant, elementInfo);
10813 _contextMenuLegacyMenu = dataDetectorsResult.get().actionProvider(menuElements);
10814 }
10815 END_BLOCK_OBJC_EXCEPTIONS
10816 return;
10817 }
10818
10819 _contextMenuLegacyMenu = menuFromLegacyPreviewOrDefaultActions(previewViewController.get(), defaultActionsFromAssistant, elementInfo);
10820
10821 } else if (_positionInformation.isImage && _positionInformation.image) {
10822 NSURL *nsURL = (NSURL *)url;
10823 RetainPtr<NSDictionary> imageInfo;
10824 auto cgImage = _positionInformation.image->makeCGImageCopy();
10825 auto uiImage = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage.get()]);
10826
10827 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:alternateURLFromImage:userInfo:)]) {
10828 NSDictionary *userInfo;
10829 nsURL = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView alternateURLFromImage:uiImage.get() userInfo:&userInfo];
10830 imageInfo = userInfo;
10831 }
10832
10833 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
10834 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:willPreviewImageWithURL:)])
10835 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView willPreviewImageWithURL:_positionInformation.imageURL];
10836
10837 RetainPtr<NSArray<_WKElementAction *>> defaultActionsFromAssistant = [_actionSheetAssistant defaultActionsForImageSheet:elementInfo.get()];
10838
10839 if (imageInfo && [uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForImage:alternateURL:defaultActions:elementInfo:)])
10840 previewViewController = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewViewControllerForImage:uiImage.get() alternateURL:nsURL defaultActions:defaultActionsFromAssistant.get() elementInfo:elementInfo.get()];
10841 else
10842 previewViewController = adoptNS([[WKImagePreviewViewController alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage defaultActions:defaultActionsFromAssistant.get() elementInfo:elementInfo.get()]);
10843 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
10844
10845 _contextMenuLegacyMenu = menuFromLegacyPreviewOrDefaultActions(previewViewController.get(), defaultActionsFromAssistant, elementInfo, _positionInformation.title);
10846 }
10847
10848 _contextMenuLegacyPreviewController = WTFMove(previewViewController);
10849}
10850
10851- (UIContextMenuConfiguration *)contextMenuInteraction:(UIContextMenuInteraction *)interaction configurationForMenuAtLocation:(CGPoint)location
10852{
10853 // Required to conform to UIContextMenuInteractionDelegate, but SPI version should be called instead.
10854 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
10855 return nil;
10856}
10857
10858- (void)_contextMenuInteraction:(UIContextMenuInteraction *)interaction configurationForMenuAtLocation:(CGPoint)location completion:(void(^)(UIContextMenuConfiguration *))completion
10859{
10860#if ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
10861 BOOL triggeredByImageAnalysisTimeout = std::exchange(_contextMenuWasTriggeredByImageAnalysisTimeout, NO);
10862#else
10863 BOOL triggeredByImageAnalysisTimeout = NO;
10864#endif
10865
10866 if (!_webView)
10867 return completion(nil);
10868
10869 if (!self.webView.configuration._longPressActionsEnabled)
10870 return completion(nil);
10871
10872 auto getConfigurationAndContinue = [weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self), interaction = retainPtr(interaction), completion = makeBlockPtr(completion), triggeredByImageAnalysisTimeout] (WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage) {
10873 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10874 if (!strongSelf || ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage == WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::Yes) {
10875 completion(nil);
10876 return;
10877 }
10878
10879 [strongSelf->_webView _didShowContextMenu];
10880
10881 strongSelf->_showLinkPreviews = true;
10882 if (NSNumber *value = [[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults] objectForKey:webkitShowLinkPreviewsPreferenceKey])
10883 strongSelf->_showLinkPreviews = value.boolValue;
10884
10885 WebKit::InteractionInformationRequest request { WebCore::roundedIntPoint([interaction locationInView:strongSelf.get()]) };
10886 request.includeSnapshot = true;
10887 request.includeLinkIndicator = true;
10888 request.disallowUserAgentShadowContent = triggeredByImageAnalysisTimeout;
10889 request.linkIndicatorShouldHaveLegacyMargins = ![strongSelf _shouldUseContextMenus];
10890
10891 [strongSelf doAfterPositionInformationUpdate:[weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(strongSelf.get()), completion] (WebKit::InteractionInformationAtPosition) {
10892 if (auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get())
10893 [strongSelf continueContextMenuInteraction:completion.get()];
10894 else
10895 completion(nil);
10896 } forRequest:request];
10897 };
10898
10899#if ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
10900 [self _doAfterPendingImageAnalysis:getConfigurationAndContinue];
10901#else
10902 getConfigurationAndContinue(WebKit::ProceedWithTextSelectionInImage::No);
10903#endif
10904}
10905
10906- (void)continueContextMenuInteraction:(void(^)(UIContextMenuConfiguration *))continueWithContextMenuConfiguration
10907{
10908 if (!self.window)
10909 return continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
10910
10911 if (!_positionInformation.touchCalloutEnabled)
10912 return continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
10913
10914 if (!_positionInformation.isLink && !_positionInformation.isImage && !_positionInformation.isAttachment && !self.positionInformationHasImageOverlayDataDetector)
10915 return continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
10916
10917 URL linkURL = _positionInformation.url;
10918
10919 if (_positionInformation.isLink && linkURL.isEmpty())
10920 return continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
10921
10922 auto uiDelegate = static_cast<id<WKUIDelegatePrivate>>(self.webView.UIDelegate);
10923
10924 if (needsDeprecatedPreviewAPI(uiDelegate)) {
10925 if (_positionInformation.isLink) {
10926 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
10927 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:shouldPreviewElement:)]) {
10928 auto previewElementInfo = adoptNS([[WKPreviewElementInfo alloc] _initWithLinkURL:linkURL]);
10929 if (![uiDelegate webView:self.webView shouldPreviewElement:previewElementInfo.get()])
10930 return continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
10931 }
10932 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
10933
10934 // FIXME: Support JavaScript urls here. But make sure they don't show a preview.
10935 // <rdar://problem/50572283>
10936 if (!linkURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily()) {
10937#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
10938 if (!WebCore::DataDetection::canBePresentedByDataDetectors(linkURL))
10939 return continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
10940#endif
10941 }
10942 }
10943
10944 _contextMenuLegacyPreviewController = nullptr;
10945 _contextMenuLegacyMenu = nullptr;
10946 _contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData = NO;
10947 _contextMenuActionProviderDelegateNeedsOverride = NO;
10948
10949 UIContextMenuActionProvider actionMenuProvider = [weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self)] (NSArray<UIMenuElement *> *) -> UIMenu * {
10950 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10951 if (!strongSelf)
10952 return nil;
10953 if (!strongSelf->_contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData)
10954 [strongSelf assignLegacyDataForContextMenuInteraction];
10955
10956 return strongSelf->_contextMenuLegacyMenu.get();
10957 };
10958
10959 UIContextMenuContentPreviewProvider contentPreviewProvider = [weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self)] () -> UIViewController * {
10960 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10961 if (!strongSelf)
10962 return nil;
10963 if (!strongSelf->_contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData)
10964 [strongSelf assignLegacyDataForContextMenuInteraction];
10965
10966 return strongSelf->_contextMenuLegacyPreviewController.get();
10967 };
10968
10969 _page->startInteractionWithPositionInformation(_positionInformation);
10970
10971 continueWithContextMenuConfiguration([UIContextMenuConfiguration configurationWithIdentifier:nil previewProvider:contentPreviewProvider actionProvider:actionMenuProvider]);
10972 return;
10973 }
10974
10975#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
10976 if ([(NSURL *)linkURL iTunesStoreURL]) {
10977 [self continueContextMenuInteractionWithDataDetectors:continueWithContextMenuConfiguration];
10978 return;
10979 }
10980#endif
10981
10982 auto completionBlock = makeBlockPtr([continueWithContextMenuConfiguration = makeBlockPtr(continueWithContextMenuConfiguration), linkURL = WTFMove(linkURL), weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self)] (UIContextMenuConfiguration *configurationFromWKUIDelegate) mutable {
10983 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
10984 if (!strongSelf) {
10985 continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
10986 return;
10987 }
10988
10989 if (configurationFromWKUIDelegate) {
10990 strongSelf->_page->startInteractionWithPositionInformation(strongSelf->_positionInformation);
10991 strongSelf->_contextMenuActionProviderDelegateNeedsOverride = YES;
10992 continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(configurationFromWKUIDelegate);
10993 return;
10994 }
10995
10996 bool canShowHTTPLinkOrDataDetectorPreview = ([&] {
10997 if (linkURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily())
10998 return true;
10999
11000 if (WebCore::DataDetection::canBePresentedByDataDetectors(linkURL))
11001 return true;
11002
11003 if ([strongSelf positionInformationHasImageOverlayDataDetector])
11004 return true;
11005
11006 return false;
11007 })();
11008
11009 ASSERT_IMPLIES(strongSelf->_positionInformation.isImage, strongSelf->_positionInformation.image);
11010 if (strongSelf->_positionInformation.isImage && strongSelf->_positionInformation.image && !canShowHTTPLinkOrDataDetectorPreview) {
11011 auto cgImage = strongSelf->_positionInformation.image->makeCGImageCopy();
11012
11013 strongSelf->_contextMenuActionProviderDelegateNeedsOverride = NO;
11014
11015 auto elementInfo = adoptNS([[_WKActivatedElementInfo alloc] _initWithInteractionInformationAtPosition:strongSelf->_positionInformation userInfo:nil]);
11016
11017 UIContextMenuActionProvider actionMenuProvider = [weakSelf, elementInfo] (NSArray<UIMenuElement *> *) -> UIMenu * {
11018 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
11019 if (!strongSelf)
11020 return nil;
11021
11022 RetainPtr<NSArray<_WKElementAction *>> defaultActionsFromAssistant = [strongSelf->_actionSheetAssistant defaultActionsForImageSheet:elementInfo.get()];
11023 auto actions = menuElementsFromDefaultActions(defaultActionsFromAssistant, elementInfo);
11024#if ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
11025 if (UIMenu *menu = strongSelf->_contextMenuForMachineReadableCode.get())
11026 [actions addObject:menu];
11027#endif // ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
11028 return [UIMenu menuWithTitle:strongSelf->_positionInformation.title children:actions];
11029 };
11030
11031 UIContextMenuContentPreviewProvider contentPreviewProvider = [weakSelf, cgImage, elementInfo] () -> UIViewController * {
11032 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
11033 if (!strongSelf)
11034 return nil;
11035
11036 return adoptNS([[WKImagePreviewViewController alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage defaultActions:nil elementInfo:elementInfo.get()]).autorelease();
11037 };
11038
11039 continueWithContextMenuConfiguration([UIContextMenuConfiguration configurationWithIdentifier:nil previewProvider:contentPreviewProvider actionProvider:actionMenuProvider]);
11040 return;
11041 }
11042
11043 // At this point we have an object we might want to show a context menu for, but the
11044 // client was unable to handle it. Before giving up, we ask DataDetectors.
11045
11046 strongSelf->_contextMenuElementInfo = nil;
11047
11048#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
11049 // FIXME: Support JavaScript urls here. But make sure they don't show a preview.
11050 // <rdar://problem/50572283>
11051 if (!canShowHTTPLinkOrDataDetectorPreview) {
11052 continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
11053 return;
11054 }
11055
11056 [strongSelf continueContextMenuInteractionWithDataDetectors:continueWithContextMenuConfiguration.get()];
11057 return;
11058#else
11059 continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(nil);
11060#endif
11061 });
11062
11063 _contextMenuActionProviderDelegateNeedsOverride = NO;
11064 _contextMenuElementInfo = wrapper(API::ContextMenuElementInfo::create(_positionInformation, nil));
11065
11066 if (_positionInformation.isImage && _positionInformation.url.isNull() && [uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:alternateURLFromImage:userInfo:)]) {
11067 UIImage *uiImage = [[_contextMenuElementInfo _activatedElementInfo] image];
11068 NSDictionary *userInfo = nil;
11069 NSURL *nsURL = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView alternateURLFromImage:uiImage userInfo:&userInfo];
11070 _positionInformation.url = nsURL;
11071 _contextMenuElementInfo = wrapper(API::ContextMenuElementInfo::create(_positionInformation, userInfo));
11072 }
11073
11074 if (_positionInformation.isLink && [uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:contextMenuConfigurationForElement:completionHandler:)]) {
11075 auto checker = WebKit::CompletionHandlerCallChecker::create(uiDelegate, @selector(webView:contextMenuConfigurationForElement:completionHandler:));
11076 [uiDelegate webView:self.webView contextMenuConfigurationForElement:_contextMenuElementInfo.get() completionHandler:makeBlockPtr([completionBlock = WTFMove(completionBlock), checker = WTFMove(checker)] (UIContextMenuConfiguration *configuration) {
11077 if (checker->completionHandlerHasBeenCalled())
11078 return;
11079 checker->didCallCompletionHandler();
11080 completionBlock(configuration);
11081 }).get()];
11082 } else if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:contextMenuConfigurationForElement:completionHandler:)]) {
11083 auto checker = WebKit::CompletionHandlerCallChecker::create(uiDelegate, @selector(_webView:contextMenuConfigurationForElement:completionHandler:));
11084 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView contextMenuConfigurationForElement:_contextMenuElementInfo.get() completionHandler:makeBlockPtr([completionBlock = WTFMove(completionBlock), checker = WTFMove(checker)] (UIContextMenuConfiguration *configuration) {
11085 if (checker->completionHandlerHasBeenCalled())
11086 return;
11087 checker->didCallCompletionHandler();
11088 completionBlock(configuration);
11089 }).get()];
11090 } else
11091 completionBlock(nil);
11092}
11093
11094#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)

11096- (void)continueContextMenuInteractionWithDataDetectors:(void(^)(UIContextMenuConfiguration *))continueWithContextMenuConfiguration
11097{
11098 BEGIN_BLOCK_OBJC_EXCEPTIONS
11099 auto ddContextMenuActionClass = getDDContextMenuActionClass();
11100 auto context = retainPtr([self dataDetectionContextForPositionInformation:_positionInformation]);
11101 RetainPtr<UIContextMenuConfiguration> configurationFromDataDetectors;
11102
11103 if (self.positionInformationHasImageOverlayDataDetector) {
11104 DDScannerResult *scannerResult = [_positionInformation.dataDetectorResults firstObject];
11105 configurationFromDataDetectors = [ddContextMenuActionClass contextMenuConfigurationWithResult:scannerResult.coreResult inView:self context:context.get() menuIdentifier:nil];
11106 } else {
11107 configurationFromDataDetectors = [ddContextMenuActionClass contextMenuConfigurationForURL:_positionInformation.url identifier:_positionInformation.dataDetectorIdentifier selectedText:[self selectedText] results:_positionInformation.dataDetectorResults.get() inView:self context:context.get() menuIdentifier:nil];
11108 _page->startInteractionWithPositionInformation(_positionInformation);
11109 }
11110
11111 _contextMenuActionProviderDelegateNeedsOverride = YES;
11112 continueWithContextMenuConfiguration(configurationFromDataDetectors.get());
11113 END_BLOCK_OBJC_EXCEPTIONS
11114}

11116#endif // ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)

11172- (void)contextMenuInteraction:(UIContextMenuInteraction *)interaction willPerformPreviewActionForMenuWithConfiguration:(UIContextMenuConfiguration *)configuration animator:(id<UIContextMenuInteractionCommitAnimating>)animator
11173{
11174 if (!_webView)
11175 return;
11176
11177 [self _stopSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:WebKit::InteractionIsHappening];
11178
11179 auto uiDelegate = static_cast<id<WKUIDelegatePrivate>>(self.webView.UIDelegate);
11180 if (!uiDelegate)
11181 return;
11182
11183 if (needsDeprecatedPreviewAPI(uiDelegate)) {
11184
11185 if (_positionInformation.isImage) {
11186 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:commitPreviewedImageWithURL:)]) {
11187 const auto& imageURL = _positionInformation.imageURL;
11188 if (imageURL.isEmpty() || !(imageURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily() || imageURL.protocolIs("data")))
11189 return;
11190 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11191 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView commitPreviewedImageWithURL:(NSURL *)imageURL];
11192 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11193 }
11194 return;
11195 }
11196
11197 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:commitPreviewingViewController:)]) {
11198 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11199 if (auto viewController = _contextMenuLegacyPreviewController.get())
11200 [uiDelegate webView:self.webView commitPreviewingViewController:viewController];
11201 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11202 return;
11203 }
11204
11205 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:commitPreviewedViewController:)]) {
11206 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11207 if (auto viewController = _contextMenuLegacyPreviewController.get())
11208 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView commitPreviewedViewController:viewController];
11209 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11210 return;
11211 }
11212
11213 return;
11214 }
11215
11216 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:contextMenuForElement:willCommitWithAnimator:)])
11217 [uiDelegate webView:self.webView contextMenuForElement:_contextMenuElementInfo.get() willCommitWithAnimator:animator];
11218 else if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:contextMenuForElement:willCommitWithAnimator:)]) {
11219 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11220 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView contextMenuForElement:_contextMenuElementInfo.get() willCommitWithAnimator:animator];
11221 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11222 }
11223
11224#if defined(DD_CONTEXT_MENU_SPI_VERSION) && DD_CONTEXT_MENU_SPI_VERSION >= 2
11225 if ([configuration isKindOfClass:getDDContextMenuConfigurationClass()]) {
11226 DDContextMenuConfiguration *ddConfiguration = static_cast<DDContextMenuConfiguration *>(configuration);
11227
11228 BOOL shouldExpandPreview = NO;
11229 RetainPtr<UIViewController> presentedViewController;
11230
11231#if defined(DD_CONTEXT_MENU_SPI_VERSION) && DD_CONTEXT_MENU_SPI_VERSION >= 3
11232 shouldExpandPreview = !!ddConfiguration.interactionViewControllerProvider;
11233 if (shouldExpandPreview)
11234 presentedViewController = ddConfiguration.interactionViewControllerProvider();
11235#else
11236 shouldExpandPreview = ddConfiguration.expandPreviewOnInteraction;
11237 presentedViewController = animator.previewViewController;
11238#endif
11239
11240 if (shouldExpandPreview) {
11241 animator.preferredCommitStyle = UIContextMenuInteractionCommitStylePop;
11242
11243 // We will re-present modally on the same VC that is currently presenting the preview in a context menu.
11244 RetainPtr<UIViewController> presentingViewController = animator.previewViewController.presentingViewController;
11245
11246 [animator addAnimations:^{
11247 [presentingViewController presentViewController:presentedViewController.get() animated:NO completion:nil];
11248 }];
11249 return;
11250 }
11251
11252 if (NSURL *interactionURL = ddConfiguration.interactionURL) {
11253 animator.preferredCommitStyle = UIContextMenuInteractionCommitStylePop;
11254
11255 [animator addAnimations:^{
11256 [[UIApplication sharedApplication] openURL:interactionURL withCompletionHandler:nil];
11257 }];
11258 return;
11259 }
11260 }
11261#endif
11262}

11264- (void)contextMenuInteraction:(UIContextMenuInteraction *)interaction willEndForConfiguration:(UIContextMenuConfiguration *)configuration animator:(nullable id<UIContextMenuInteractionAnimating>)animator
11265{
11266 if (!_webView)
11267 return;
11268
11269 [self _stopSuppressingSelectionAssistantForReason:WebKit::InteractionIsHappening];
11270
11271 // FIXME: This delegate is being called more than once by UIKit. <rdar://problem/51550291>
11272 // This conditional avoids the WKUIDelegate being called twice too.
11273 if (_contextMenuElementInfo) {
11274 auto uiDelegate = static_cast<id<WKUIDelegatePrivate>>(self.webView.UIDelegate);
11275 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:contextMenuDidEndForElement:)])
11276 [uiDelegate webView:self.webView contextMenuDidEndForElement:_contextMenuElementInfo.get()];
11277 else if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:contextMenuDidEndForElement:)]) {
11278 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11279 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView contextMenuDidEndForElement:_contextMenuElementInfo.get()];
11280 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11281 }
11282 }
11283
11284 _page->stopInteraction();
11285
11286 _contextMenuLegacyPreviewController = nullptr;
11287 _contextMenuLegacyMenu = nullptr;
11288 _contextMenuHasRequestedLegacyData = NO;
11289 _contextMenuElementInfo = nullptr;
11290
11291#if ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
11292 _contextMenuForMachineReadableCode.clear();
11293#endif // ENABLE(IMAGE_ANALYSIS)
11294
11295 [animator addCompletion:[weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKContentView>(self)] () {
11296 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
11297 if (!strongSelf)
11298 return;
11299 [strongSelf _removeContextMenuViewIfPossible];
11300 [strongSelf->_webView _didDismissContextMenu];
11301 }];
11302}
11303
11304#endif // USE(UICONTEXTMENU)

11306- (BOOL)_interactionShouldBeginFromPreviewItemController:(UIPreviewItemController *)controller forPosition:(CGPoint)position
11307{
11308 if (!_longPressCanClick)
11309 return NO;
11310
11311 WebKit::InteractionInformationRequest request(WebCore::roundedIntPoint(position));
11312 request.includeSnapshot = true;
11313 request.includeLinkIndicator = true;
11314 request.linkIndicatorShouldHaveLegacyMargins = !self._shouldUseContextMenus;
11315 if (![self ensurePositionInformationIsUpToDate:request])
11316 return NO;
11317 if (!_positionInformation.isLink && !_positionInformation.isImage && !_positionInformation.isAttachment)
11318 return NO;
11319
11320 const URL& linkURL = _positionInformation.url;
11321 if (_positionInformation.isLink) {
11322 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = static_cast<id <WKUIDelegatePrivate>>([_webView UIDelegate]);
11323 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11324 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:shouldPreviewElement:)]) {
11325 auto previewElementInfo = adoptNS([[WKPreviewElementInfo alloc] _initWithLinkURL:(NSURL *)linkURL]);
11326 return [uiDelegate webView:self.webView shouldPreviewElement:previewElementInfo.get()];
11327 }
11328 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11329 if (linkURL.isEmpty())
11330 return NO;
11331 if (linkURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily())
11332 return YES;
11333#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
11334 if (WebCore::DataDetection::canBePresentedByDataDetectors(linkURL))
11335 return YES;
11336#endif
11337 return NO;
11338 }
11339 return YES;
11340}
11341
11342- (NSDictionary *)_dataForPreviewItemController:(UIPreviewItemController *)controller atPosition:(CGPoint)position type:(UIPreviewItemType *)type
11343{
11344 *type = UIPreviewItemTypeNone;
11345
11346 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = static_cast<id <WKUIDelegatePrivate>>([_webView UIDelegate]);
11347 BOOL supportsImagePreview = [uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:commitPreviewedImageWithURL:)];
11348 BOOL canShowImagePreview = _positionInformation.isImage && supportsImagePreview;
11349 BOOL canShowLinkPreview = _positionInformation.isLink || canShowImagePreview;
11350 BOOL useImageURLForLink = NO;
11351 BOOL respondsToAttachmentListForWebViewSourceIsManaged = [uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_attachmentListForWebView:sourceIsManaged:)];
11352 BOOL supportsAttachmentPreview = ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_attachmentListForWebView:)] || respondsToAttachmentListForWebViewSourceIsManaged)
11353 && [uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:indexIntoAttachmentListForElement:)];
11354 BOOL canShowAttachmentPreview = (_positionInformation.isAttachment || _positionInformation.isImage) && supportsAttachmentPreview;
11355 BOOL isDataDetectorLink = NO;
11356#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
11357 isDataDetectorLink = _positionInformation.isDataDetectorLink;
11358#endif
11359
11360 if (canShowImagePreview && _positionInformation.isAnimatedImage) {
11361 canShowImagePreview = NO;
11362 canShowLinkPreview = YES;
11363 useImageURLForLink = YES;
11364 }
11365
11366 if (!canShowLinkPreview && !canShowImagePreview && !canShowAttachmentPreview)
11367 return nil;
11368
11369 const URL& linkURL = _positionInformation.url;
11370 if (!useImageURLForLink && (linkURL.isEmpty() || (!linkURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily() && !isDataDetectorLink))) {
11371 if (canShowLinkPreview && !canShowImagePreview)
11372 return nil;
11373 canShowLinkPreview = NO;
11374 }
11375
11376 auto dataForPreview = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
11377 if (canShowLinkPreview) {
11378 *type = UIPreviewItemTypeLink;
11379 if (useImageURLForLink)
11380 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataLink] = (NSURL *)_positionInformation.imageURL;
11381 else
11382 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataLink] = (NSURL *)linkURL;
11383#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
11384 if (isDataDetectorLink) {
11385 NSDictionary *context = nil;
11386 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_dataDetectionContextForWebView:)])
11387 context = [uiDelegate _dataDetectionContextForWebView:self.webView];
11388
11389 DDDetectionController *controller = [getDDDetectionControllerClass() sharedController];
11390 NSDictionary *newContext = nil;
11391 RetainPtr<NSMutableDictionary> extendedContext;
11392 DDResultRef ddResult = [controller resultForURL:dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataLink] identifier:_positionInformation.dataDetectorIdentifier selectedText:[self selectedText] results:_positionInformation.dataDetectorResults.get() context:context extendedContext:&newContext];
11393 if (ddResult)
11394 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataDDResult] = (__bridge id)ddResult;
11395 if (!_positionInformation.textBefore.isEmpty() || !_positionInformation.textAfter.isEmpty()) {
11396 extendedContext = adoptNS([@{
11397 getkDataDetectorsLeadingText() : _positionInformation.textBefore,
11398 getkDataDetectorsTrailingText() : _positionInformation.textAfter,
11399 } mutableCopy]);
11400
11401 if (newContext)
11402 [extendedContext addEntriesFromDictionary:newContext];
11403 newContext = extendedContext.get();
11404 }
11405 if (newContext)
11406 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataDDContext] = newContext;
11407 }
11408#endif // ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
11409 } else if (canShowImagePreview) {
11410 *type = UIPreviewItemTypeImage;
11411 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataLink] = (NSURL *)_positionInformation.imageURL;
11412 } else if (canShowAttachmentPreview) {
11413 *type = UIPreviewItemTypeAttachment;
11414 auto element = adoptNS([[_WKActivatedElementInfo alloc] _initWithType:_WKActivatedElementTypeAttachment URL:(NSURL *)linkURL imageURL:(NSURL *)_positionInformation.imageURL location:_positionInformation.request.point title:_positionInformation.title ID:_positionInformation.idAttribute rect:_positionInformation.bounds image:nil]);
11415 NSUInteger index = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView indexIntoAttachmentListForElement:element.get()];
11416 if (index != NSNotFound) {
11417 BOOL sourceIsManaged = NO;
11418 if (respondsToAttachmentListForWebViewSourceIsManaged)
11419 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataAttachmentList] = [uiDelegate _attachmentListForWebView:self.webView sourceIsManaged:&sourceIsManaged];
11420 else
11421 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataAttachmentList] = [uiDelegate _attachmentListForWebView:self.webView];
11422 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataAttachmentIndex] = [NSNumber numberWithUnsignedInteger:index];
11423 dataForPreview.get()[UIPreviewDataAttachmentListIsContentManaged] = [NSNumber numberWithBool:sourceIsManaged];
11424 }
11425 }
11426
11427 return dataForPreview.autorelease();
11428}

11430- (CGRect)_presentationRectForPreviewItemController:(UIPreviewItemController *)controller
11431{
11432 return _positionInformation.bounds;
11433}

11435- (UIViewController *)_presentedViewControllerForPreviewItemController:(UIPreviewItemController *)controller
11436{
11437 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = static_cast<id <WKUIDelegatePrivate>>([_webView UIDelegate]);
11438
11439 [_webView _didShowContextMenu];
11440
11441 NSURL *targetURL = controller.previewData[UIPreviewDataLink];
11442 URL coreTargetURL = targetURL;
11443 bool isValidURLForImagePreview = !coreTargetURL.isEmpty() && (coreTargetURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily() || coreTargetURL.protocolIs("data"));
11444
11445 if ([_previewItemController type] == UIPreviewItemTypeLink) {
11446 _longPressCanClick = NO;
11447 _page->startInteractionWithPositionInformation(_positionInformation);
11448
11449 // Treat animated images like a link preview
11450 if (isValidURLForImagePreview && _positionInformation.isAnimatedImage) {
11451 RetainPtr<_WKActivatedElementInfo> animatedImageElementInfo = adoptNS([[_WKActivatedElementInfo alloc] _initWithType:_WKActivatedElementTypeImage URL:targetURL imageURL:nil location:_positionInformation.request.point title:_positionInformation.title ID:_positionInformation.idAttribute rect:_positionInformation.bounds image:_positionInformation.image.get()]);
11452
11453 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForAnimatedImageAtURL:defaultActions:elementInfo:imageSize:)]) {
11454 RetainPtr<NSArray> actions = [_actionSheetAssistant defaultActionsForImageSheet:animatedImageElementInfo.get()];
11455 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11456 return [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewViewControllerForAnimatedImageAtURL:targetURL defaultActions:actions.get() elementInfo:animatedImageElementInfo.get() imageSize:_positionInformation.image->size()];
11457 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11458 }
11459 }
11460
11461 RetainPtr<_WKActivatedElementInfo> elementInfo = adoptNS([[_WKActivatedElementInfo alloc] _initWithType:_WKActivatedElementTypeLink URL:targetURL imageURL:nil location:_positionInformation.request.point title:_positionInformation.title ID:_positionInformation.idAttribute rect:_positionInformation.bounds image:_positionInformation.image.get()]);
11462
11463 auto actions = [_actionSheetAssistant defaultActionsForLinkSheet:elementInfo.get()];
11464 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(webView:previewingViewControllerForElement:defaultActions:)]) {
11465 auto previewActions = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
11466 for (_WKElementAction *elementAction in actions.get()) {
11467 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11468 WKPreviewAction *previewAction = [WKPreviewAction actionWithIdentifier:previewIdentifierForElementAction(elementAction) title:[elementAction title] style:UIPreviewActionStyleDefault handler:^(UIPreviewAction *, UIViewController *) {
11469 [elementAction runActionWithElementInfo:elementInfo.get()];
11470 }];
11471 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11472 [previewActions addObject:previewAction];
11473 }
11474 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11475 auto previewElementInfo = adoptNS([[WKPreviewElementInfo alloc] _initWithLinkURL:targetURL]);
11476 if (UIViewController *controller = [uiDelegate webView:self.webView previewingViewControllerForElement:previewElementInfo.get() defaultActions:previewActions.get()])
11477 return controller;
11478 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11479 }
11480
11481 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11482 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForURL:defaultActions:elementInfo:)])
11483 return [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewViewControllerForURL:targetURL defaultActions:actions.get() elementInfo:elementInfo.get()];
11484
11485 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForURL:)])
11486 return [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewViewControllerForURL:targetURL];
11487 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11488
11489 return nil;
11490 }
11491
11492 if ([_previewItemController type] == UIPreviewItemTypeImage) {
11493 if (!isValidURLForImagePreview)
11494 return nil;
11495
11496 RetainPtr<NSURL> alternateURL = targetURL;
11497 RetainPtr<NSDictionary> imageInfo;
11498 RetainPtr<CGImageRef> cgImage = _positionInformation.image->makeCGImageCopy();
11499 RetainPtr<UIImage> uiImage = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage.get()]);
11500 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:alternateURLFromImage:userInfo:)]) {
11501 NSDictionary *userInfo;
11502 alternateURL = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView alternateURLFromImage:uiImage.get() userInfo:&userInfo];
11503 imageInfo = userInfo;
11504 }
11505
11506 RetainPtr<_WKActivatedElementInfo> elementInfo = adoptNS([[_WKActivatedElementInfo alloc] _initWithType:_WKActivatedElementTypeImage URL:alternateURL.get() imageURL:nil location:_positionInformation.request.point title:_positionInformation.title ID:_positionInformation.idAttribute rect:_positionInformation.bounds image:_positionInformation.image.get() userInfo:imageInfo.get()]);
11507 _page->startInteractionWithPositionInformation(_positionInformation);
11508
11509 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11510 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:willPreviewImageWithURL:)])
11511 [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView willPreviewImageWithURL:targetURL];
11512 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11513
11514 auto defaultActions = [_actionSheetAssistant defaultActionsForImageSheet:elementInfo.get()];
11515 if (imageInfo && [uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:previewViewControllerForImage:alternateURL:defaultActions:elementInfo:)]) {
11516 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
11517 UIViewController *previewViewController = [uiDelegate _webView:self.webView previewViewControllerForImage:uiImage.get() alternateURL:alternateURL.get() defaultActions:defaultActions.get() elementInfo:elementInfo.get()];
11518 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
11519 if (previewViewController)
11520 return previewViewController;
11521 }
11522
11523 return adoptNS([[WKImagePreviewViewController alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage defaultActions:defaultActions elementInfo:elementInfo]).autorelease();
11524 }
11525
11526 return nil;
11527}

11530{

11532 if ([_previewItemController type] == UIPreviewItemTypeImage) {
11533 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:commitPreviewedImageWithURL:)]) {
11534 const URL& imageURL = _positionInformation.imageURL;

11536 return;

11601- (NSArray *)_presentationRectsForPreviewItemController:(UIPreviewItemController *)controller
11602{
11603 if (_positionInformation.linkIndicator.contentImage) {
11604 auto origin = _positionInformation.linkIndicator.textBoundingRectInRootViewCoordinates.location();
11605 return createNSArray(_positionInformation.linkIndicator.textRectsInBoundingRectCoordinates, [&] (CGRect rect) {
11606 return [NSValue valueWithCGRect:CGRectOffset(rect, origin.x(), origin.y())];
11607 }).autorelease();
11608 } else {
11609 float marginInPx = 4 * _page->deviceScaleFactor();
11610 return @[[NSValue valueWithCGRect:CGRectInset(_positionInformation.bounds, -marginInPx, -marginInPx)]];
11611 }
11612}

11645{

11684
11685// FIXME: Overriding isEqual: without overriding hash will cause trouble if this ever goes into an NSSet or is the key in an NSDictionary,
11686// since two equal items could have different hashes.
11687- (BOOL)isEqual:(id)other
11688{
11689 if (![other isKindOfClass:[WKTextRange class]])
11690 return NO;
11691
11692 WKTextRange *otherRange = (WKTextRange *)other;
11693
11694 if (self == other)
11695 return YES;
11696
11697 // FIXME: Probably incorrect for equality to ignore so much of the object state.
11698 // It ignores isNone, isEditable, selectedTextLength, and selectionRects.
11699
11700 if (self.isRange) {
11701 if (!otherRange.isRange)
11702 return NO;
11703 return CGRectEqualToRect(self.startRect, otherRange.startRect) && CGRectEqualToRect(self.endRect, otherRange.endRect);
11704 } else {
11705 if (otherRange.isRange)
11706 return NO;
11707 // FIXME: Do we need to check isNone here?
11708 return CGRectEqualToRect(self.startRect, otherRange.startRect);
11709 }
11710}
11711
11712@end

11725// FIXME: Overriding isEqual: without overriding hash will cause trouble if this ever goes into a NSSet or is the key in an NSDictionary,
11726// since two equal items could have different hashes.
11727- (BOOL)isEqual:(id)other
11728{
11729 if (![other isKindOfClass:[WKTextPosition class]])
11730 return NO;
11731
11732 return CGRectEqualToRect(self.positionRect, ((WKTextPosition *)other).positionRect);
11733}
